{{Dzinu-sia}} {{ɣleti le ƒea me}} '''[[Siamlɔm]] 2007''' enye ɣleti adrelia le ƒea me. Edze egɔme le [[Kɔsiɖagbe]] dzi eye awu enu le ŋkeke 31 megbe le [[Brãɖagbe]] dzi. ==Ŋkeke tɔxewo le ɣleti sia me== * [[Siamlɔm 1]] - Canada Ŋkeke ([[Canada]]) * [[Siamlɔm 1]] - Siamlɔm Ŋde ([[Bulgaria]]) * [[Siamlɔm 1]] - Republik Ŋkeke ([[Ghana]]) * [[Siamlɔm 4]] - Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[United States]]) * [[Siamlɔm 5]] - Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[Venezuela]]) * [[Siamlɔm 6]] - Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[Malawi]]) * [[Siamlɔm 7]] - Saba Saba Ŋkeke, [[Tanzania]] * [[Siamlɔm 7]] - San Fermin ([[Pamplona]] kple [[Spain]]) * [[Siamlɔm 7]] - Tanabata ([[Japan]]) * [[Siamlɔm 9]] - Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[Argentina]]) * [[Siamlɔm 14]] - Bastille Ŋkeke ([[France]]) * [[Siamlɔm 20]] - Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[Colombia]]) * [[Siamlɔm 21]] - Racial Harmony Day ([[Singapore]]) * [[Siamlɔm 24]] - Tisha B'Av ([[Jewish]]) * [[Siamlɔm 25]] - Commonwealth Day ([[Puerto Rico]]) * [[Siamlɔm 28]] - Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[Peru]]) ==Nusiwo yi dzi le ɣleti sia me== *TAM Linhas Aéreas ƒe ayameʋu A320 ɖeka do le mɔ dzi le Brazil eye wòle dzo enumake. Emenɔlawo katã ku. *[[w:en:Giorgio Napolitano|'''Giorgio Napolitano''']] si nye [[Italia]] dukplɔla la va sra [[Ghana]] ŋkeke etɔ̃. *[[Switzerland]] dukplɔla, [[w:en:Micheline Calmy-Rey|'''Aƒenɔ Micheline Calmy-Rey''']] va sra [[Ghana]] ŋkeke eve. *[[Roger Federer]] ɖu [[Rafael Nadal]] dzi 7–6, 4–6, 7–6, 2–6, 6–2. Esiae enye ƒe atɔ̃lia tri ɖe enu si me Federer ɖu dzi le [[Wimbledon]]. *'''[[Georgina Theodora Wood]]''', si nye Ghana ƒe nyɔnu gbãtɔ si zu Ʋɔnudrɔ̃la Gãtɔ la xɔ dzesi si woyɔna be Order of the Star of Ghana, le Gɛ̃ le Siamlɔm 6, 2007. Esiae nye Ghana dukɔa ƒe bubu kɔkɔtɔwu si wonaa dukɔamenɔlawo. *'''[[African Union]]''' ƒe takpekpe asiekelia wu nu le Gɛ̃ Siamlɔm 4, 2007. * Wodze ga yeyea ŋdɔ wɔwɔm le [[Ghana]]. Woawɔ '''[[Ghanaian cedi]]''' yeyea kple ga xoxoa katã ŋudɔ vaseɖe Dzome 2007 hafi woaɖe asi le xoxoa ŋu susue. Wogbaa GH¢ 1 yeyea na 10,000 cedi xoxoawo.

Edo liƒo kple [[Côte d'Ivoire]], [[Ghana]], [[Togo]] kpakple [[Benin]] le eƒe anyigbe lɔƒo, [[Niger]] le eƒe ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo, kple [[Mali]] le eƒe dzigbe. Dukɔ sia ƒe ŋkɔ xoxoa enye [[Dahomey]]. Burkina Faso ƒe dugã enye [[Ouagadougou]]. Gbe si wogblɔna le dɔwɔƒewo enye [[Fransegbe]].

'''Afɔfiɛ''' (alo '''April''') enye ɣleti enelia le ƒea me. Ɣleti sia le [[Gregoria ɣletigbãle]]a me. Ŋkeke 30 ye le ɣleti sia kpakple etɔ̃ bubuwo me.
Ɣleti sia ƒe ŋkɔ ɖeka tso ''Aprilis'' le [[Latingbe]] me. Egɔme enye ''aperire'' alo ʋuʋum elabena ɣeyiɣi sia me seƒoƒowo tsena le wo de. [[Helatɔ]]wo hã yɔna ɣeyiɣi sia be ἁνοιξις (ʋuʋum). Esime Romatɔwo tsɔ woƒe mawuwo ƒe ŋkɔwo na ɣletiawo ta la, wobui be woyɔne be ''Aprilis'' si tso Helatɔwo ƒe mawuawo ɖeka [[Afrodite]] ƒe ŋkɔme.
''[[Anglo-Saxontɔ]]wo'' tsɔ ŋkɔ na ɣleti sia be ''Oster-monath'' alo ''Eostur-monath'' si nye woƒe mawu ɖeka ''Eostre'' alo ''Ostara'' ƒe ŋkɔ. Ŋkɔ sia me ''Easter'' tso.

'''Anyɔnyɔ''' (alo '''September''') enye ɣleti asiekelia le ƒea me le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke 30 ye le ɣletia me.
Le Latingbe me la, ''septi'' gɔme enye adre eye ''septem'' gɔme enye adrelia. Le [[Roma ɣletigbalẽ]]a me la, Anyɔnyɔ alo September enye ɣleti adrelia vaseɖe ƒe 153 BC.
== Nu tɔxewo le Anyɔnyɔ me == [[File:Sapphire01.jpg|thumb|right|Safirwo]] * Sukuwo geɖe ƒe ƒewo dzea egɔme le ɣleti sia me. * Woɖoa ŋku [[Anyɔnyɔ 1]] dzi abe ŋkeke si dzi Eritreatɔwo dze woƒe ƒe 30 aʋa na ɖokuisinɔnɔ tso Ethiopia tɔwo gbɔ. * [[Anyɔnyɔ 11]] enye ''Patriots Day'' le ''United States'' dukɔa me eye emake enye ŋkeke si dzi wo ku ayameʋuwo de dziƒoxɔwo me le ƒe 2001 me. * [[Anyɔnyɔ 16]] eye [[Mexico]] dukɔa ƒe [[Ɖokuisinɔnɔ ŋkeke]]. * Le [[KwaZulu-Natal]] la, woɖoa ŋku fia [[Shaka]] dzi le Kɔsiɖagbe susueame le Anyɔnyɔ me. * [[Germany]] dukɔa ɖua ''Oktoberfest'' alo Kele zã eye [[China]] dukɔa hã ɖua Dasiamime Ɣleti zã le Anyɔnyɔ me. * Le [[Australia]] la, woɖua ''Father's Day'' alo Tɔwo ƒe ŋkeke le ɣleti sia ƒe Kɔsiɖagbe gbãtɔ dzi.
== Nu bubuwo == [[File:Morning Glory Flower.jpg|thumb|right|''Morning glory'' seƒoƒo]] * Ƒe sia ƒe me la, Anyɔnyɔ kple [[Dzome]] dzea egɔme le ŋkeke ɖeka dzi le kɔsiɖaa me. * Ɣleti sia ƒe [[seƒoƒo]] tɔxe enye ''Morning glory'' le Eŋlisigbe me. * Anyɔnyɔ ƒe kpe xɔasi enye [[safir]]. * [[Xexemeʋa evelia]] dze egɔme [[Anyɔnyɔ 1]], [[1939]] le esime [[Adolf Hitler]] wɔ avu kpli [[Poland]]. Ewu enu le [[Anyɔnyɔ 2]], [[1945]] le esime [[Japan]] dukɔa tsi asi.
== Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe == * [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=September&oldid=145011859 September le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me]
== Nuxexlẽwo le teƒe bubuwo == * [[:en:Sapphire|Safir le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me]] * [[:en:Morning glory|''Morning glory'' le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me]]

== Nusiwo yi edzi gbemagbe == * [[1687]] – [[Isaac Newton]] publishes ''[[Philosophiae Naturalis Principia Mathematica]]''. * [[1811]] - [[Venezuela]] xɔ ɖokuisinɔnɔ tso [[Spain]] gbɔ. * [[1830]] - [[France]] ho aʋa ɖe [[Algeria]] ŋu. * [[1865]] - The Salvation Army is founded in the East End of London, England. * [[1975]] - [[Arthur Ashe]] zu ameyibɔ gbãtɔ si ɖu dzi le [[Wimbledon]] le ŋutsuwo ƒe hame. * [[1978]] - [[Fred Akuffo]] zu [[Ghana dukplɔlawo|Ghana dukplɔla]]
== Azãgbewo == * [[Venezuela]]: [[Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke]] ([[1811]]). * [[Algeria]]: Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[1962]]). * [[Cape Verde]]: Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[1975]]). * [[Armenia]]: [[Constitution Day]] ([[1995]]) * [[Czechia]] and [[Slovakia]]: [[Saints Cyril and Methodius]] wovae ɖo [[Great Moravia]] ([[863]] lɔƒo). * [[Isle of Man]]: [[Tynwald Day]] ([[1266]]). * [[United States]]: [[Bloody Thursday]], [[Longshoremans Union Holiday]].

[[File:The National Archives UK - CO 1069-50-1.jpg|thumb|Kwame Nkrumah]] '''Kwame Nkrumah''' ([[Anyɔnyɔ 21]], [[1909]] - [[Afɔfiɛ 27]], [[1972]]) enye [[Ghana]] vidzidzi gbãtɔ si vaye zu [[Ghana dukplɔlawo|Ghana dukplɔla]].
== Eƒe ɖevime kple sukudede == Wodzi Nkrumah le [[Nkroful]] le Ghana ƒe [[Ɣetoɖoƒe nutome]]. Ŋkɔ si wotsɔ ne le eƒe ɖevime enye '''Francis Nwia Kofi Ngonloma'''. Ede [[Achimota School]] le Gẽ hafi wòyi edzi le Roma Katolik suku me le [[Axim]]. Le ƒe 1935 me la, ezɔ mɔ heyi ɖe [[United States]]. Ede [[Lincoln yunivesiti]], afisi woxɔ BA ɖaseɖigbãle le.
== Eƒe gbɔgbɔ va Ghana == Le 1945 me la, Nkrumah gbɔ va Ghana. Le eƒe gbɔgbɔ ko la, woɖoe nuŋlɔ̃la na [[United Gold Coast Convention]] (UGCC). Woƒe nunɔla ɣemaɣi enye [[J. B. Danquah]]. Le ƒe ʋea ɖewo megbe la, vovototo va ge ɖe wome eye Nkrumah do le UGCC la me eye wò va ɖo eya ŋutɔ ƒe dunyaheha si nye [[Convention People's Party]] (CPP). Wo nɔ [[United Kingdom]] dukɔa biam na Ghana ƒe ɖokuisinɔnɔ.
== Ghana ƒe ɖokuisinɔnɔ == Le [[Tedoxe 6]], [[1957]] me la, Ghana dukɔa xɔ ɖokuisinɔnɔ eye Nkrumah zu dukɔa kplɔla. [[Fianyɔnu Elizabet II]] ganɔ zia dzi na Ghana ƒe etɔ̃ sɔ̃ŋ hafi eya hã trɔ tso [[Siamlɔm 1]], [[1960]] dzi.
== Eƒe dziɖuɖu == Nkrumah tu nuwo geɖe abe tɔdziʋudzeƒe gãaɖe, ayameʋudzeƒe yeye kple [[Akosombo Dam]]. Nkrumah nye Ghana dukplɔla ƒe 9 sɔŋ hafi wo ge le zia dzi. Ghana asrafowo tso ɖe eŋu le esime Ghana nɔ sesem.
== Nkrumah ƒe ƒometɔwo == Nkrumah nɔ ŋkɔ enye Aƒenɔ Nyaniba. Vi ene ye nɔ Nkrumah si. Via tsitsitɔ enye ''Francis'', si nye dɔyɔla kple amatsiwɔla de ŋgɔ le Ghana. Emegbe la, Nkrumah ɖe Fathia Rezhik, si tso Egyipté. Wodzi vi etɔ̃. Gbãtɔ enye ŋutsu, Gamel, evelia enye Samia, si nye nyɔnu eye mamlea enye Sekou si nye ŋutsu.
== Kwame Nkrumah ƒe agbalẽwo == * ''Ghana: The Autobiography of Kwame Nkrumah'' (1957) ISBN 0-901787-60-4 * ''Africa Must Unite'' (1963) ISBN 0-901787-13-2 * ''African Personality'' (1963) * [http://www.marxists.org/subject/africa/nkrumah/neo-colonialism/index.htm ''Neo-Colonialism: the Last Stage of Imperialism''] (1965) ISBN 0-901787-23-X * ''Axioms of Kwame Nkrumah'' (1967) ISBN 0-901787-54-X * ''[http://www.marxists.org/subject/africa/nkrumah/1967/african-socialism-revisited.htm African Socialism Revisited]'' (1967) * ''Voice From Conakry'' (1967) ISBN 90-17-87027-3 * ''Handbook for Revolutionary Warfare'' (1968) * ''Consciencism: Philosophy and Ideology for De-Colonisation'' (1970) ISBN 0-901787-11-6 * ''Class Struggle in Africa'' (1970) ISBN 0-901787-12-4 * ''The Struggle Continues'' (1973) ISBN 0-901787-41-8 * ''I Speak of Freedom'' (1973) ISBN 0-901787-14-0 * ''Revolutionary Path'' (1973) ISBN 0-901787-22-1

'''Kɔsiɖagbe''' enye ŋkeke si le [[Memleɖagbe]] kple [[Dzoɖagbe]] dome. [[Kristotɔwo]] tsɔe abe ŋkeke gbãtɔ le kɔsiɖaa me. Yuropatɔwo bue abe ŋkeke mamlea le kɔsiɖaa me.
Le dukɔwo geɖe me la, Kɔsiɖagbe enye mɔkeke na dɔwɔlawo.
Le [[Gregoria ɣletigbãle]]a me la, ƒeawo dzea edzi ƒe alafa ene sia. Yudatɔwo ƒe ƒeyeye medzena Kɔsiɖagbe dzi gbeɖe o. Le ɣleti ɖesiaɖe si dzea egɔme le Kɔsiɖagbe me la, ŋkeke wuietɔ̃lia dzena Fiɖagbe dzi.
{{Ŋkekewo le kɔsiɖaa me}}

Dzoɖagbe le [[Blugbe]] me enye ''Ɛdwoada'' si de sɔsɔ gbe kple Eʋegbe tɔ. Le [[Yuropa]] duwo geɖe me la, Dzoɖagbe enye ŋkeke gbãtɔ le kɔsiɖaa me.

[[File:Nicaea icon.jpg|thumb|right|Nutata si fia ''Nicea'' takpekpe gbãtɔ]] '''Xɔsemeʋuʋu''' ([[Latingbe]]: ''Symbolum Apostolorum''), enye nyawo si ɖe xɔse siwo nɔ Kristotɔwo si le blema ŋɔ̃li la fia. Kritso hame geɖe le xexeame egbe zãa xɔsemeʋuʋua abe nufafia na tsitadede kple subɔsubɔa ŋutɔ ƒe akpa vevie dometɔawo ɖeka. Hameawo aɖewo wonye Roma Katolico hame, Anglikan alo Eŋlisi hame, Presbyteria hame kple Metoɖist hame nyuiewo.
Woxɔese be woŋlɔ xɔsemeʋuʋua elabena ameaɖewo nɔ fafiam bena ɖe ko wodze abe [[Yesu]] nye amegbetɔ gake menye amegbetɔ wònye hafi o eye ahatso wò nye be wo hee ɖe ati ŋu eye wò ku. Xɔsemeʋuʋua ƒe nyawo fia nusiwo dzi Kristotɔwo xɔse fitaa na nusrɔ̃lawo kple amewo katã.
== Eme nyawo == ==Xɔsemeʋuʋu le Eʋegbe me== :Mexɔ Mawu, etɔa ŋusẽ katã tɔ, :si wɔ dzi kple anyigba dzi se.
:Mexɔ Yesu Kristo, Mawu ƒe tenuvi ɖeka, si nye mía aƒetɔ dzi se, :Ame si ƒe fu wofɔ tso Gbɔgbɔ Kɔkɔe la me, :Eye Maria, dzetugbui la dzii, :Ame si kpe fu le Pontio Pilato te, :Eye wohee ɖe ati ŋu, eye wòku, eye woɖii; :Ame si yi tsiẽƒe, :Eye wòga fɔ tso amekukuwo dome le ŋkeke etɔ̃a gbe, :Eye wòyi dziƒo, :Eye wònɔ etɔa ŋusẽ katã tɔ ƒe nuɖusi me. :Afima wòa ɖa tso ava drɔ̃ ʋɔnu na amegbagbewo kple amekukuwo.
:Mexɔ Gbɔgbɔ Kɔkɔe dzi se, :Kple Kristo hame kɔkɔea ɖeka, :Si nye amekɔkɔewo ƒe ƒomedodo, :Nuvɔ̃wo ɖeɖe, :Ŋutilãa ƒe tsitretsitsi, :Kpakple agbemavɔ̃ dzi se. :Amen.
{{col-begin}} {{col-2}} === Nyawo le Latingbe me === ;Symbolum Apostolorum :Credo in Deum Patrem omnipotentem, :Creatorem caeli et terrae.
:Et in Iesum Christum, Filium Eius unicum, Dominum nostrum, :qui conceptus est de Spiritu Sancto, :natus ex Maria Virgine, :passus sub Pontio Pilato, :crucifixus, mortuus, et sepultus, :descendit ad ínferos, :tertia die resurrexit a mortuis, :ascendit ad caelos, :sedet ad dexteram Dei Patris omnipotentis, :inde venturus est iudicare vivos et mortuos.
:Credo in Spiritum Sanctum, :sanctam Ecclesiam catholicam, :sanctorum communionem, :remissionem peccatorum, :carnis resurrectionem, :vitam aeternam. :Amen. {{col-2}} === Nyawo le Helagbe me === <small>''Nuŋɔŋlɔwo le afia le blema Helagbe me, eye wome ŋlɔe ɖe egbeviwo ƒe gbegbɔgblɔ nu o.''</small>
:Πιστεύω εις θεòν πατέρα παντοκράτορα, :ποιητην ουρανου και γης.
:Και εις Ιησουν Χριστòν, υιον αυτου τòν μονογενη, τòν κύριον ημων, τòν συλληφθέντα εκ πνεύματος αγίου, :γεννηθέντα εκ Μαρίας της παρθένου, :παθόντα επι Ποντίου Πιλάτου, :σταυρωθέντα, θανόντα, και ταφέντα, :κατελθόντα εις τά κατώτατα, :τη τρίτη ημέρα αναστάντα απò των νεκρων, :ανελθόντα εις τους ουρανούς, :καθεζόμενον εν δεξια θεου πατρος παντοδυνάμου, :εκειθεν ερχόμενον κριναι ζωντας και νεκρούς.
:Πιστεύω εις τò Πνευμα τò Αγιον, :αγίαν καθολικην εκκλησίαν, :αγίων κοινωνίαν, :αφεσιν αμαρτιων, :σαρκος ανάστασιν, :ζωην αιώνιον. :Αμήν. :''("Triglot Concordia", St. Louis: Concordia Publishing House, 1921, p. 12)'' {{col-end}} == Nyawo le Eŋlisigbe me == {{col-begin}} {{col-2}} === Book of Common Prayer === :I believe in God the Father Almighty, Maker of heaven and earth;
:And in Jesus Christ his only Son our Lord, :Who was conceived by the Holy Ghost, :Born of the Virgin Mary, :Suffered under Pontius Pilate, :Was crucified, dead, and buried, :He descended into hell; :The third day he rose again from the dead, :He ascended into heaven, :And sitteth on the right hand of God the Father Almighty; :From thence he shall come to judge the quick and the dead.
:I believe in the Holy Ghost; :The holy Catholick <!-- This is the spelling used in the Book of Common Prayer. DO NOT CHANGE. -->Church; :The Communion of Saints; :The Forgiveness of sins; :The Resurrection of the body, :And the life everlasting. :Amen. {{col-2}} === Common Worship === :I believe in God, the Father almighty, :creator of heaven and earth.
:I believe in Jesus Christ, his only Son, our Lord, :who was conceived by the Holy Spirit, :born of the Virgin Mary, :suffered under Pontius Pilate, :was crucified, died, and was buried; :he descended into hell. :On the third day he rose again; :he ascended into heaven, :he is seated at the right hand of the Father, :and he will come to judge the living and the dead.
:I believe in the Holy Spirit, :the holy catholic Church, :the communion of saints, :the forgiveness of sins, :the resurrection of the body, :and the life everlasting. :Amen. {{col-end}}

'''Gali''' enye nuɖuɖu si bɔ le [[Afrika]] ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo. Wotɔna gali tso [[agbeli]] me.
==Gali tɔtɔ== [[Image:Manihot esculenta dsc07325.jpg|thumb|agbeli si wotsɔ wɔa gali]]<!--nutata le afia-------------------------------------------------------->
Hafi woa tɔ gali la, wohona agbeli tso agble me. Wokpana agbelia eye le eyome la, woklɔnae kple tsi bena ɖia katã na kɔ le eŋuti. Le esia megbe la, wolina agbelia vaseɖe esime wòa me. Le elili megbe la, wozia agbelia le kotokuwo me eye wodana kpewo ɖe kotokuawo dzi hena tsia fafia tso eme. Esia yina edzi abe ŋkeke eve lɔƒo eye le nuwuwua la, agbelia hã tsi.
Ne tsia vɔ le eme la, wo srana agbelia alebe wonɔna wuliwuli. Ne wowɔ esia vɔ la, wotɔna galia le gaze gã wo me le dzo dzi. Wometsɔna ami tɔnae o. Ne wòƒu nyuie la, ekema étɔ vɔ eye woateŋu adze ezãzã gɔme.
==Eɖuɖu== Nuɖuɖu siwo tso gali me sɔgbɔ. Wodena gali tsi me kple sukli kple notsi. Esia wɔwɔ mesẽ kroa o eye tsidede gali bɔ le sukuwo me ŋutɔ le [[Ghana]] kple [[Nigeria]]. Bubu enye gali bublu kple atadi alo dzetsi eye woateŋu aɖui enumake. Wotɔna gali hã le ami me tsɔ wɔna nuɖuɖu vovovowoe abe [[agbeli kaklo]]. Wodena tsi dzodzoe gali hã eye woblunae le dzodzi abe akple ene. Nigeriatɔwo yɔnae be [[eba]]. Woɖuna esia kple dzetsi alo tsiƒoƒo. [[Image:PeeledCassava.jpg|thumb|Agbeli kpakpa le tsi me.]]<!--nutata le afia---------------------------------------------------------------------->
==Aɖi si le agbeli me== Aɖi si Eŋlisiawo yɔna be ''cyanide'' le agbeli me. Dɔlele si woyɔna be "''tropical ataxic neuropathy''" bɔ le afisiwo agbeliɖuɖu bɔ le.<ref>[http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/tandf/cijf/2002/00000053/00000004/art00008 Loss of residual cyanogens in a cassava food during short-term storage] Onabolu A.O.; Oluwole O.S.A.; Bokanga M.. ''International Journal of Food Sciences and Nutrition'', Volume 53, Number 4, 1 July 2002 , pp. 343-349(7)</ref> Dɔlele sia naa amewo ƒe lãme gbana eye zɔzɔ kple tsitretsitsi sena ŋutɔ. Wokpɔ be ne wowɔ galia ŋudɔ nyuie la, aɖia geɖe doa tso eme eye mega nana dɔlele o.<ref>[http://diss.kib.ki.se/2001/91-628-4894-1/ Cassava processing, consumption and dietary cyanide exposure] Onabolu, Adeyinka (7 september 2001) ''Doktorsavhandling vid Karolinska Institutet''</ref>

revision.text:
'''Presbyteria Nyanyui Hame le Ghana''' enye Kristo subɔsubɔ hame ɖeka le [[Ghana]]. Amegeɖe ga yɔnae be "'''''E.P. Church'''''" elabena eƒe ŋkɔ le [[Eŋlisigbe]] me enye ''Evangelical Presbyterian Church''.
==Hamea ɖoɖo== Hamea ƒe ɖoɖo dze egɔme kple Germania kristotɔwo si woyɔna be ''Norddeutsche Mission'' tso Bremen le [[Germany]] kple ''Basel Mission'' dɔwɔlawo. Ha eve siawo tso wode va Afrika va nɔ Mawunya dɔ wɔm le [[Eʋeawo]] dome tso ƒe 1847 me. Le [[Xexemeʋa gbãtɔ]] ŋɔli la, hame eve nɔ [[Eŋlisiawo]] te le ''[[Gold Coast]]'' eye hame adre nɔ Franseawo ƒe akpadzi le ''[[Togoland]]''. Ha gbãtɔ woɖo nɔ ''Mission Tɔve''.<ref>[http://www.reformiert-online.net/adressen/detail.php?lg=eng&id=13334 Eglise évangélique presbytérienne du Togo] ''Address data base of Reformed churches and institutions.'' Reformed Online</ref> Le aʋa sia ƒe nuwuwu la, woma dukɔ evee. Ɣetoɖloƒe nɔ Eŋlisiawo te eye ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo nɔ Franseawo te. Wowɔ hameawo ƒe sinɔɖ gbãtɔ le Damɛ 1922 me. Togbɔ be woma Togo nyigba le ɣemaɣi gɔ̃ɔ̃ɔ hã la, wowɔ sinɔɖ la le Eʋe hamea katã nu.
Le ƒe 1923 me la, mawudɔwɔlawo tso [[Skotland]] va nɔ dɔwɔm le Eŋlisi Togo kpa dzi. Afisia ye zu [[Vɔlta nutome]] le Ghana fifia. Fransedodo hame nɔ Paris hamea te. Mama sia va li ke, eye hameawo va zu hame eve blibowo. Hame eveawo ga wɔna sewo ɖeka ŋudɔ. Wo ame eveawo kpea ƒe ene sia ene le sinɔɖ ɖeka ko vaseɖe fifia.<ref>[http://www.reformiert-online.net/adressen/detail.php?lg=eng&id=12200 Presbyteria Nyanyui Hame le Ghana] ''Address data base of Reformed churches and institutions.'' Reformed Online</ref>
==Hamea ƒe dɔwɔƒe gãtɔ== Hamea ƒe dɔwɔƒe gãtɔ le [[Ho]], si nye Vɔlta nutome dugã la. Ame abe 600,000 ye le hamea me fifia eye ha 750 lɔƒo woɖo vadeɖe fifia. Nunɔla tsitsitɔ enye mɔɖeretɔ.<ref>[http://www.warc.ch/24gc/04.html Our hosts] World Alliance of Reformed Churches.</ref>
==Sukuwo== Hamea ɖo sukuwo le Vɔlta nutoame zã. Suku ɖeka si xɔ ŋkɔ ntɔ enye Mawuli Secondary suku le Ho. Amesiwo ɖo suku sia enye Aƒetɔ kple Aƒenɔ Trost, amesiwo nye mawudɔwɔlawo tso ''United Church of Christ''.<ref name=gm>[http://www.globalministries.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=348&Itemid=28 General Ministries] Global Ministries (7 October 2005).</ref>
==Dɔyɔƒewo== Dɔyɔƒewo hã le hamea si. Ɖeka enye Adidome Hospital.<ref name=gm/>
==Kristo hamewo si do ƒome kple E.P. Hamea== *Eglise évangélique presbytérienne du Togo *''[[:en:Lippische Landekirche]]'' *''[[:en:Church of Scotland|Church of Scotland]]'' *''[[:de:Bremische Evangelische Kirche|Bremische Evangelische Landeskirche|]]'' (''le Dzama Wikipiɖia la me'') *''[[:en:United Reformed Church|United Reformed Church]]'' - Osɔfo ɖeka tsoa E. P. Hamea alo ''Presbyterian Church of Ghana'' vayi wɔa dɔ kpli wo ƒe ene sia ene.<ref>[http://www.urc.org.uk/our_work/committees/ecumenical/news/autmn_2001.htm United Reformed Church gbeƒãɖeɖewo]</ref>
==Hadedewo== E. P. Hamea de ha kple Kristo habɔbɔwo le xexeame godoo. Wodemtɔao ɖewo wonye: *''[[:en:Christian Council of Ghana|Christian Council of Ghana]]'' *''[[:en:World Alliance of Reformed Churches|World Alliance of Reformed Churches]]'' *''[[:en:World Reformed Communion|World Reformed Communion]]''
==Nyawo ƒe tsoƒe== <references/>
==Nuxexlẽwo le teƒe bubuwo== *[http://www.reformiert-online.net/adressen/detail.php?lg=eng&id=12200 Presbyteria Nyanyui Hame le Ghana] (''Eŋlisigbe me'') *[http://www.reformiert-online.net/adressen/detail.php?lg=eng&id=13334 Eglise évangélique presbytérienne du Togo] (''Eŋlisigbe me'') *[http://warc.jalb.de/warcajsp/church.jsp?news_id=19&navi=9&church=12200 Presbyteria Nyanyui Hame le Ghana ƒe nyaɖewo] (''Eŋlisigbe me'') *[http://www.globalministries.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=348&Itemid=28 Global Ministries of the Christian Church (Disciples of Christ) and the United Church of Christ] (''Eŋlisigbe me'') *[http://www.urc.org.uk/our_work/committees/ecumenical/news/autmn_2001.htm News from the Ecumenical Committee (United Reformed Church)] (''Eŋlisigbe me'')

'''Brãɖagbe''' enye ŋkeke si le [[Dzoɖagbe]] kple [[Kuɖagbe]] dome le kɔsiɖaa me. Eƒe ŋkɔ le Yevugbewo me tso woƒe mawuwo ƒe ŋkɔ me.
Brãɖagbe le [[Blugbe]] me enye ''Ɛbenada'' si de sɔsɔ gbe kple Eʋegbe tɔ. Le [[Yuropa]] duwo geɖe me la, Brãɖagbe enye ŋkeke evelia le kɔsiɖaa me.
Le [[Eŋlisigbe]] me la, woyɔnae be ''Tuesday'', si tso ''Scandinavia'' mawu siwoyɔna be ''Tyr'' ƒe ŋkɔ me. Le [[Latingbe]] me la, woyɔnae be ''Martis dies''.
{{Ŋkekewo le kɔsiɖaa me}}

revision.text:
[[File:Janus-Vatican.jpg|thumb|right|''Ianus'' ƒe nɔnɔme si wome daɖi le ''Vatican Museum'']] '''Dzove''' (alo '''Yanuar''') enye ɣleti gbãtɔ le ƒea me le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke blaetɔ-vɔ-ɖeka ye le ɣletia me. Le ɣleti siame la, pepi dona eye gbewo hã bina dzo.
Le blema ŋɔli la, Romatɔwo xɔese be ''Ianus'' nye mawu na agbowo, ʋɔtruwo, gɔmedzedzewo kple nuwuwuwo. Le esiata la, wotsɔ ŋkɔ na ɣleti gbãtɔ le ƒea me be ''Ianuarius'' si tso ''ianua'' si nye ʋɔtru le [[Latingbe]] me.
Tedoxe enye ɣleti gbãtɔ le blema ŋɔli gake tso ƒe 153 BC la, Romatɔwo trɔe, eye Dzove va zu ɣleti gbãtɔ.
== Ŋkeke tɔxewo le Dzove me == [[File:GarnetCrystalUSGOV.jpg|thumb|right|Kpe si woyɔna be ''garnet'' le Eŋlisigbe me]] * [[1789]] - Wotia Amerika dukplɔla gbãtɔ. * [[1946]] - ''[[United Nations]]'' wɔ woƒe takpekpe gbãtɔ le [[London]].
=== Mɔkekewo === * Ƒe yeye Ŋkeke - Dzove ƒe ŋkeke gbãtɔ * Martin Luther King Ŋkeke le [[United States]] - Dzoɖagbe etɔ̃lia * Australia Ŋkeke le [[Australia]] - Dzove 26 * Republic Ŋkeke le [[India]] - Dzove 26
== Nu bubuwo == [[File:Gartennelke 1.jpg|thumb|right|''Carnation'' seƒoƒo]] * Ɣleti sia ƒe [[seƒoƒo]] tɔxewo wonye "''carnation''" kple "''snowdrop''" le Eŋlisigbe me. * Dzove ƒe kpe xɔasi enye kpe si woyɔna le Eŋlisigbe me be ''garnet''.
== Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe == * [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/January Dzove le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me]

<center> {| width="60%" style="border:1px solid black" | <inputbox> type=search bgcolor=#eeeeff# buttonlabel=Yi (Di tanya sia) searchbuttonlabel=Dii </inputbox> |} </center> "Yi (Di tanya sia)" tatia akɔ wò ayi axa yeye dzi kple tanya si sɔ kple esi wòŋlɔ ɖe goa me, negbe axaa ɖe li kpakple tanya mawo xoxo ko. Teƒe le axa yeye sia dzi si wòateŋu atia na kpekpeɖeŋu kple nuwoŋlɔŋlɔ ne anɔ hahiãm na wò. Mehiã be na gbugbɔ ava afii na axa yeye gɔmedzedze o. Woateŋu adze wo gɔme kple nuŋɔŋlɔ dzẽwo tatia. Megavɔ̃ na nuyeyewo gɔmedzedze kroa o.
Ne wòle nuyeye gɔmedzem la, ɖo ŋku edzi be: * Tanya si wòtia le vevie ŋutɔ, elabena eya ye le tanya zu gbe na axaa kat. * Enyo wu be wòdzra ɖo nyuie hafi gɔmedzedzea, elabena ebɔbɔ wu vodadawo ɖɔɖɔɖo le emegbe. * Ɖo ŋku nusiwo woɖe mɔ na le Wikipiɖia la dzi. * Kpɔe ɖa gbã be woŋlɔ nusi wòadi be yeaŋlɔ xoxo kple tanya bubua ɖe mahã. * Ne nye ɖe ko wòadi be yea doe akpɔ gbã la, ekema yi [[Wikipedia:Sandbox|''Keme'']] gbã.
[[m:Help:User rights|Mɔnana]] ɖeka si woateŋu ana [[Template:Status|ŋdɔwɔlawo]] enye be woaɖe mɔ nawo be "''createpage''", si ana wòateŋu adze nuŋɔŋlɔ yeye gɔme. Wikia ateŋu ana mɔ sia si wo me xe mɔ na xoxo o (esia enye [[m:Help:User_rights#Defaults|default]]), alo ana amewo si ŋlɔ ŋkɔ.
''Kpekpeɖeŋu na nuwotrɔtrɔ'' le afisiafi si wòa nɔ dɔ wɔm lw eyata mele bubu ge o. <!-- For general editing matters and details on the [[w:markup language|markup language]] of the [[Help:Filling the page|wikitext]], see [[Help:Editing]]. ''If you want to experiment, use the [[{{ns:4}}:Sandbox|sandbox]] first.'' Note: Sandbox page is currently blank. The purpose of this blank page is to use as a whiteboard to experiment. --><!-- Anyone, including you, can write these help documents at [[m:Help:Contents]], and you are most likely allowed to edit the site, {{SITENAME}} that you are looking at now! Just type a title in the box at the bottom of the page, click "Create article", and start writing. You should probably create a link to the article in a related page; linking to a page is enough to "create" the page! New pages can also be started by following a link to a non-existent page, which likewise launches the edit page. See [[#Starting a page through the URL|Starting a page through the URL]] below. --> == Nya veviewo == * '''[[Help:Didim|Dii]]''' nakpɔe ɖa be amea ɖe ŋlɔ numaa xoxoa hafi nadze tɔwò gɔme. Gbɔdzi ɖi na tia tanya nyuie. *Gbugbɔ to ese si wo kuɖe nusi wòadi be yeaŋlɔ la ŋu e.g.: **alesi wonaa nkɔwo; kpɔ [[Help:Page name]]. **axa yeye ga hiã, alo manyo be na ŋlɔ nua atsɔ atɔ ɖe bubu si le xoxo nu oa? Enyo wu be nu kpuiwo na tɔ ɖe bubuwo nu wu be nadze yeyea gɔme ko. Ne eva didi akpa la, woateŋu ama eme evee. **Le esime ne le nua ŋlɔm la, kpɔ <u>Ƒomedodowo</u> ɖa le axaa dzi. Kpɔ egbɔ bena axa lɔ̃ kpakple esiwo doƒome kplii. **Ne nuaɖeke mele afima o la, ekema axa sia nye tsɔ̃evi eye ehiã be na na axa bubuwo na doƒome kplii.
==Axa yeye gɔme dzedze tso ƒomedodo dzi alo le edidi vɔ megbe== Wòateŋu adze axa yeye gɔme kple ƒomedodo dzẽ tatia. Esia atsɔ wò ayi axa yeye dzi kple tanya si sɔ kpakple esi ne tia la, eye wòateŋu adze nuŋɔŋlɔm gɔme enumake.
== Axa gbɔlo wɔwɔ == Axa yeye to vovo na axa gbɔlo: [[Help:Page history|axa ƒe dzidzimenyawo]] le gbɔloɔ si. Axa yeye gɔmedzedze le abe asitrɔtrɔ le axa gbɔlo ŋuti ene, negbe axa yeye fiaa nyawo tso [[MediaWiki:Newarticletext]]. Ɣeaɖewoɣi la, axa gbɔlo wɔwɔ dea ame dzi - le kpɔɖeŋu me, woateŋu awɔ "template" alebe ne nuaɖewo le alo meli o la, aŋlɔ nya kpuia ɖe ko alo afɔ nububwo kpee.

Wòle ŋugbe dom na mí bena wò ŋutɔe ŋlɔ nusiawo, alo etsɔe tso afisi mɔɖeɖe li fãa be amesiame na tsɔ nuwo tso afima fãa. MEGA DA NUSIWO ŊU MƆƉEƉE MELI NA O ƉE AFISIA O!

[[File:Améthystre sceptre2.jpg|thumb|right|Kpe xɔasi si woyɔna le Eŋlisigbe me be ''amethyst'']] [[File:5p pwy pansies.jpg|thumb|right|''Violet'' (Eŋlisigbe)]] [[File:Primula-vulgaris-flowers.jpg|thumb|right|''Primrose'' (Eŋlisigbe)]] '''Dzodze''' (alo '''Februar''') enye ɣleti evelia le ƒea me le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Eyae nye kpuitɔ wu le ɣletiawo katã me. Ŋkeke 28 ye le ɣletia me, gake le ƒe ene sia ene megbe la, ŋkeke 29 ye le eme.
Februar ŋkɔa tso ''februum'' le [[Latingbe]] me si gɔme enye kɔkɔ. Februar ŋkeke 15 enye gbe si wo kɔa nuwo ŋuti le [[Romatɔwo]] ƒe blema ŋɔli wo.
== Ŋkeke tɔxewo le Dzodze me == * [[Groundhog Day]] / [[Candlemas]] ([[Dzodze 2]]) * ''Constitution Ŋkeke'' ([[Mexico]]) ([[Dzodze 5]]) * ''Waitangi'' Ŋkeke, [[New Zealand]] ([[Dzodze 6]]) * ''[[Abraham Lincoln]]'' ƒe dzigbe ([[Dzodze 12]]) * ''[[St. Valentine Ŋkeke]]'' ([[Dzodze 14]]) * [[Aflaga Ŋkeke (Canada)|Aflaga Ŋkeke]] - [[Canada]] ([[Dzodze 15]]) * [[Kim Jong-Il]] ƒe dzigbe, ([[Dzodze 16]]) * Fia Harald ƒe dzigbe ([[Norway]]) ([[Dzodze 21]]) * ''[[International Mother Language Day]]'' ([[Dzodze 21]]) * ''Thinking Day'' (Girl Guides) ([[Dzodze 22]]) * ''B.P. Ŋkeke'' (Skout Habɔbɔ [[Canada]]) ([[Dzodze 22]]) * ''Founder's Day'' (Skout Habɔbɔ (UK)) ([[Dzodze 22]]) * Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke ([[Dominican Republic]]) ([[Dzodze 27]]) * ''Massacre Day'', (Taiwan) (Dzodze 28) * [[George Washington|Washington Ŋkeke]] (Dzoɖa etɔ̃lia)
== Nya bubuwo == * Ŋkeke gbãtɔ le Dzodze, [[Tedoxe]] kple [[Adeɛmekpɔxe]] me dzea ŋkeke ɖeka dzi le kɔsiɖaa me. * Ɣleti sia ƒe kpe xɔasi enye esi woyɔna be ''amethyst'' le [[Eŋlisigbe]] me. * Dzodze seƒoƒo tɔxewo nye ''violet'' (Eŋlisigbe) kple ''primrose'' (Eŋlisigbe).
== Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe == * [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=February&oldid=150895589 Dzodze le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me] - Dasiamime 13, 2007
{{Ɣletiawo le ƒea me}}

[[File:EleanorRooseveltHumanRights.png|thumb|250px|right|[[Eleanor Roosevelt]] kple Amegbetɔ ƒe Ablɔɖevinyenye ŋu Kpeɖoɖodzinyawo le Spaingbe me.]] '''Amegbetɔ ƒe Ablɔɖevinyenye ŋu Kpeɖoɖodzinya''' enye kpeɖoɖodzinyawo si [[Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo ƒe Takpekpegã]] la ŋlɔ daɖi le [[10 Dzome]] [[1948]] le [[Palais de Chaillot]], [[Paris]]. Ɖoɖo 30 le eme si dzi [[Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo]] da asi ɖo na amegbetɔwo katã le xexeame godoo.
"Wodzi amegbetɔwo katã ablɔɖeviwoe eye wodzena bubu kple gomekpɔkpɔ sɔsɔe. Susu kple dzitsinya le wo dometɔ ɖesiaɖe si eyata wodze be woanɔ anyi le ɖekawɔwɔ blibo me." — ''Kpeɖodzinya ɖoɖo I''
== Eŋɔŋlɔ == Le nuvɔ̃ɖi siwo [[Adolf Hitler]] kple eƒe asrafowo wɔ le [[Xexemeʋa evelia]] me ta la, amewo geɖe va bui be ehiã be woaŋlɔ sewo le amegbetɔwo ƒe ablɔɖevinyenye ŋuti. Esia na be [[Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo ƒe Nuŋlɔlagã]] tia [[John Peters Humphrey]] si tso [[Canada]] be wòakpɔ eŋɔŋlɔ dzi. Amesiwo kpe ɖe eŋu wodome tɔa ɖewo enye [[Eleanor Roosevelt]] tso [[United States]], [[Jacques Maritain]] kple [[René Cassin]] tso [[France]], [[Charles Malik]] tso [[Lebanon]], kple [[P. C. Chang]] tso [[China]]. Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo ƒe Takpekpegã si kpe le 10 Dzome 1948 wɔ akametatia le nya sia ŋuti, eye dukɔ 48 lɔ ɖe dzi, 0 gbe, eye 8 mede dzesia ɖeke o.[http://www.americanrhetoric.com/speeches/eleanorrooseveltdeclarationhumanrights.htm Eleanor Roosevelt Address to the United Nations General Assembly] 9 Dzome 1948, le Paris, France. == Emenyawo == Woŋlɔe abe dukɔ me sewo ene eye wodze egɔme kple Kpɔkplɔyiɖeme. Wokplɔ esia ɖo kpli ɖoɖo 30 sɔ̃. == Gbewo == Woŋlɔ ɖe ''[[Guinness Book of Records]]'' la me be nyasiawo nye agbalẽ si gɔme woɖe ɖe gbe bubuwo me wòsɔgbɔ wu le xexeame.[http://portal.unesco.org/education/fr/file_download.php/6bbab6974c53987ab4fb801fb8b8abfaUN_decade_HR.pdf United Nations Decade for Human Rights Education (1995-2004)]7 Anyɔnyɔ 2000. [[Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo ƒe Takpekpegã]]. [[Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo]] ŋutɔ ɖe nya siawo gɔme ɖe gbe 366 me.[http://www.unhchr.ch/udhr/navigate/alpha.htm Alphabetical Listing of All Translations (366)] OHCHR. == Nyasiawo ƒe tsoƒe == == Nuxexlẽwo le teƒe bubuwo == * [http://www.unhchr.ch/udhr/lang/ewe.htm Amegbetɔ ƒe Ablɔɖevinyenye ŋu Kpeɖoɖodzinya menyawo] == Kpeɖeŋu nyawo == * Metsɔ nya siawo ƒe akpa gãtɔ tso [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Universal_Declaration_of_Human_Rights&oldid=150925593 Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la dzi] le 13 Dasiamime 2007. [[Category:Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo]]

[[File:Emerald specimen with matrix.jpg|thumb|right|Kpe xɔasi si woyɔna be ''emerald''.]] '''Damɛ''' (alo '''Mai''') enye ɣleti atɔ̃lia le ƒea me le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke 31 ye le ɣletia me.
Helatɔwo tsɔ woƒe mawu ''Maia'' ƒe ŋkɔ na ɣleti sia. Romatɔwo bui abe vidzidzi mawu ene eye woyɔnae be Bona Dea. Wonɔ eƒe zã ɖum le ɣletia me.
== Ŋkeke tɔxewo le Damɛ me == === Mɔkekewo === * [[Damɛ 1]]: - [[May Day]] alo [[Damɛ Ŋkeke]] alo [[Dɔwɔlawo ƒe ŋkeke]] * Le dukɔ geɖe me la, [[May Day]] alo [[Damɛ Ŋkeke]] le [[Damɛ 1]] dzi. Woɖunae abe [[Labor Day]] alo [[Dɔwɔlawo Ŋkeke]]le dukɔ geɖe me. * Le [[United Kingdom]] la, [[May Day]] nye [[Damɛ 1]], gake woɖuna mɔkekea le Dzoɖagbe gbãtɔ dzi le Damɛ me. * "Finland's Day" le [[Finland]] dze Damɛ 12lia dzi.
=== Nusiwo menɔna ŋkeke ɖeka dzi o === [[File:Convallaria majalis l.jpg|thumb|left|Seƒoƒo si Eŋlisiawo yɔna be ''Lily of the Valley'']] * [[Ɣedzeƒe Kristotɔwo]] ɖua [[Easter]] le kɔsiɖa ɖeka le [[Afɔfiɛ 4]] kple [[Damɛ 8]] lia dzi. * Ne ɣleti le ɖiɖim le Damɛ me la, woɖua ''[[Vesak]]'' si ɖoa ŋku [[Siddhartha Gautama]] ƒe dzidzi, agbenɔnɔ kple ku dzi. * Le [[Canada]] la, woɖua [[Victoria Ŋkeke]] le [[Dzoɖagbe]] si do ŋgɔ alo dze [[Damɛ 24]] dzi. Le [[Quebec]] la, woyɔe be ''[[National Patriotes Day]]''.
Memleɖagbe gbãtɔ * [[Kentucky Derby]] le [[Kentucky]], [[United States]].
Kɔsiɖagbe evelia * enye [[Vinɔwo Ŋkeke]] le [[Anguilla]], [[Aruba]], [[Australia]], [[Austria]], [[Bahamas]], [[Barbados]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Belgium]], [[Belize]], [[Bermuda]], [[Bonaire]], [[Brazil]], [[Brunei]], [[Canada]], [[Chile]], [[Colombia]], [[Cuba]], [[Croatia]], [[Curaçao]], [[Czechia]], [[Denmark]], [[Ecuador]], [[Estonia]], [[Finland]], [[Germany]], [[Greece]], [[Grenada]], [[Honduras]], [[Hong Kong]], [[Iceland]], [[India]], [[Italy]], [[Jamaica]], [[Japan]], [[Latvia]], [[Malta]], [[Malaysia]], [[Netherlands|The Netherlands]], [[New Zealand]], [[Peru]], [[Philippines]], [[Puerto Rico]], [[Singapore]], [[Slovakia]], [[South Africa]], [[Suriname]], [[Switzerland]], [[Taiwan]], [[Trinidad and Tobago]], [[Turkey]], [[United States]], [[Uruguay]], [[Venezuela]], [[Zimbabwe]].
Fiɖagbe gbãtɔ * [[No Pants Day]]
Memleɖagbe evelia * Woɖua [[World Fair Trade Day]]
Dzoɖagbe mamlea * [[United States]] - Woƒe [[Memorial Day]] le [[Damɛ 30]], gake woɖunae le Dzoɖagbe mamlea dzi le Damɛ me.
== Nu bubuwo == [[File:Luscinia megarhynchos Istria 01.jpg|thumb|right|Xe si woyɔna be ''nightingale'' le Eŋlisigbe me.]] Ɣletia ƒe [[xe]] tɔxe enye esi Eŋlisiawo yɔna be ''nightingale''. [[Seƒoƒo]] tɔxewo enye ''Lily of the Valley'' kple ''Common Hawthorn'' le Elisigbe me. Kpe xɔasi na ɣletia enye ''emerald'' le Eŋlisigbe me.
== Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe == * [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=May&oldid=150814504 Damɛ le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me]
{{Ɣletiawo le ƒea me}}

[[File:Alexandrite 26.75cts.jpg|thumb|right|Alexandrite kpewo]] '''Masa''' (alo '''Yuni''') enye ɣleti adelia le ƒea me le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke 30 ye le ɣletia me.
Le blema ŋɔli la, [[Romatɔwo]] tsɔ [[Yuno]] si nye woƒe mawu ɖeka ƒe ŋkɔ na ɣleti sia. [[Helatɔwo]] yɔna mawu sia be [[Hera]] (Ήρα) {{IPA|[ˈhiːrə]}} le [[Helagbe]] me.
== Ŋkeke tɔxewo le Masa me == * [[Aflaga Ŋkeke]]wo le [[Sweden]] ([[Masa 6]]), [[United States]] ([[Masa 14]]), [[Denmark]] ([[Masa 15]]), [[Argentina]] ([[Masa 20]]), and [[Romania]] ([[Masa 26]]). * [[Masa 16]] enye ''Youth Day'' alo "Ɖekakpuiwo ƒe ŋkeke" le [[South Africa]]. * ''Wimbledon Tennis'' hoʋiʋlia nɔa ɣleti sia me. * [[Philippines]] dukɔa ƒe ɖokuisinɔnɔ ŋkeke dze [[Masa 12]] dzi. * [[Eritrea]] [[Masa 20]] nye "''Martyrs Day''" .
=== Nusiwo menɔna ŋkeke ɖeka dzi o === * [[Vitɔwo ƒe Ŋkeke]] :* Kɔsiɖagbe evelia le Masa me le [[Belgium]]. Le [[United States]], [[United Kingdom]], Mexico, [[Netherlands]], [[Ireland]] kple [[Canada]] la, woɖuie le Kɔsiɖagbe etɔ̃lia dzi le Masa me.
== Nu bubuwo == * Ɣleti aɖeke meli si ƒe ŋkeke gbãtɔ dzea esi dzi Masa tɔ dzea le kɔsiɖaa me.
== Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe == * [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=June Masa le Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me] * Ɣletia ƒe seƒoƒo enye ''rose'' alo ''honeysuckle'' le [[Eŋlisigbe]] me. * Masa ƒe kpe xɔasi enye ''[[:en:pearl|pearl]]'', ''[[:en:Alexandrite|Alexandrite]]'', or [[:en:Orthoclase|''moonstone'']].
{{Ɣletiawo le ƒea me}}
[[Category:Ɣletiwo]] [[Category:Masa]]

[[Image:Heckert GNU white.svg|right|150px]] '''{{BASEPAGENAME}}, woezɔ ɖe Eʋe Wikipiɖia loo!'''! Akpe na nusiwo wòwɔ le Eʋe Wikipiɖia la dzi! Mexɔese be wòkpɔe be Eʋegbe ŋlɔlawo wo me sɔgbɔ ɖe afisia o. Míele mɔ kpɔm be wòateŋu akpe ɖe mía ŋu. Ne wò mese Eʋegbe nyuie aɖe o hã la, megblẽ kroa o. Megavɔ̃ o, mɔxexea ɖeke meli o. Wòateŋu adze nuwo ŋɔŋlɔ gɔme fifia gɔ̃ hã. Ne wòle xaxaa ɖe me la, wòateŋu abiam fãa le [[User talk:Natsubee|'''afisia''']] . Ɣesiaɣi wòŋlɔ nua ɖe la, ɖo ŋku dzi na da dzesi sia (~~~~) ɖe eɖome. Esia ada ŋkɔ wò (alo dzesi wò), ŋkekea kpakple gaƒoƒoa si neŋlɔe katã ɖe nuŋɔŋlɔawo gɔme. Míe me kpɔ ŋlɔ kpekpeɖeŋu nyawo haɖeke o. Ne ele kpekpeɖeŋu dim la, biam le [[User talk:Natsubee|'''afisia''']] alo ne wòse gbe siawo la, kpɔ Wikipiɖia siawo ƒe kpekpeɖeŋu nyawo ɖa: *[[Template:Woezɔ/Inglisigbe|English]] | [[Template:Woezɔ/Fransegbe|Français]] | [[Template:Woezɔ/Dzamagbe|Deutsch]]. '''Ayekoo na wò! Netsɔ!'''!

[[File:Anglospeak(800px).png|300px|right|thumb|Eŋlisigbe]] '''Eŋlisigbe''' enye gbe si tso [[England]] eye wogblɔnae le dukɔwo me zã. Dukɔawo dometɔa ɖewo enye [[Australia]], [[Canada]], [[Ireland]], [[New Zealand]] kple [[United States]]. Wodona Eŋlisigbe le dɔwɔƒewo le dukɔwo siwo dzi Eŋlisiawo ɖu vayi le [[Afrika]] kple [[Asia]] katã.
[[Afrika]] dukɔ aɖe siwo doa Eŋlisigbe lawoe nye [[Ghana]], [[Nigeria]], [[Eritrea]], [[Gambia]], [[Kenya ]], [[Lesotho]], [[Liberia]], [[Malawi]], [[Namibia]], [[Rwanda]], [[South Africa]], [[South Sudan]], [[Sudan]], [[Swaziland]], [[Tanzania]], [[Uganda]], [[Zambia]], [[Zimbabwe]].

[[File:LocationSierraLeone.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Coat of arms of Sierra Leone.svg|right|150px]] [[File:Flag of Sierra Leone.svg|right|200px|border]] '''Sierra Leone''' enye dukɔ si le [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] kpadzi lɔƒo. Edo liƒo kple [[Liberia]] le eƒe ɣedzeƒe kpadzi, eye [[Guinea]] ƒo xlãae tso eƒe ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo vayi eƒe dzigbe. Aƒu si woyɔna be [[{{SIL|Atlantic Ocean}}]] la le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo. Sierra Leone ƒe dugã enye [[Freetown]], si gɔme enye "ablɔɖe du". Gbe si wogblɔna le dɔwɔƒewo le dua me enye [[Eŋlisigbe]], elabena Eŋlisiawo ɖu wodzi vayi.
{{Afrika dukɔwo}} <!--Gbe bubuwo-->

revision.text:
==Eʋegbe Wikipiɖia la ƒe ''Interface'' gɔmeɖeɖe== Ehiã be míaɖe nuŋɔŋlɔwo (alo ''System messages)'' siwo le Eʋe Wikipiɖia la me ɖe Eʋegbe me. Medze wo gɔmeɖeɖe xoxo. Zi alesi vovototowo sɔgbɔ le Eʋegbe dodo me ta la, ɖewomahĩ anɔ eme bena menye wo katã yea de bliboe o. Mɔ li fãa be na ɖɔ esiwo le afisia ɖo eye ne ele Wikipiɖia la zam eye ne kpɔ bubuwo hã la, de dzesi wo le afima alo afia ne mía trɔ asi le woŋu. Míave mianu bena miakpe ɖe míaŋu na Eʋegbe Wikipiɖia la na de to. Akpe na mi katã.--[[User:Natsubee|Natsubee]] 10:35, 4 Anyɔnyɔ 2007 (UTC)
===Translation of the Ewe Wikipedia Interface=== The system messages of the Ewe Wikipedia Interface need to be translated into the Ewe language. I have started with some of them already. As you are well aware however, there are many variations to the Ewe language and my translations may not always be the best ones. Please fill free to add to or change the suggestions below. If you come across some of the system messages already done and feel there is a better translation, please note it on the talk page of the particular translation in the Mediawiki talk namespace or on here. Thanks for your cooperation.--[[User:Natsubee|Natsubee]] 10:35, 4 Anyɔnyɔ 2007 (UTC)
===Traduction de l'interface de la Wikipedia en éwé=== Les messages système de l'interface de la Wikipedia en éwé doivent être traduits en langue d'éwé. J'ai déjà commencé par certains d'entre eux. Comme vous en êtes bien averti cependant, il y a beaucoup de variations à la langue d'éwé et mes traductions peuvent ne pas être toujours les meilleures. Vous pouvez ajouter ou bien changer les suggestions ci-dessous. Si vous trouvez certaines traductions des messages système déjà faits et vous croyez qu'il y a une meilleure traduction, notez-la sur la page d'entretien de la traduction particulière dans le namespace d'entretien de Mediawiki ou dessus ici. Merci pour votre coopération. (Pouvez vous m'excuser - Je ne parle pas le français très bien. Merci.--[[User:Natsubee|Natsubee]] 10:35, 4 Anyɔnyɔ 2007 (UTC)

Wotsɔ nyasiawo tso Iŋlisi Wikipiɖia la me. Ne nyaa ɖe me mekɔ o alo vovototoa ɖe le wo me la, tsɔ [[:en:Wikipedia:General disclaimer|Iŋlisi tɔ]] gbɔ. Míegale asi trɔm le afisia ŋuti.
Ne wòmese Eʋegbe nyuie o la, wòa kpɔ gbe bubuwo ƒe nuxlɔame nyawo le miame le afisi woŋlɔ ɖa be "le gbe bubuwo me" la te.
---- __NOTOC__
WIKIPIƉIA MEDO ŊUGBEA ƉEKE BENA NUSIANU LE EME VAVÃ O
'''Wikipiɖia''' enye nunyagbãle si li fãa na amewo katã ƒe zazã, eye wònye ame vovowo kple habɔbɔ vovowo siwo na kpekpeɖeŋu le dɔsia ŋɔŋlɔm le xexeme nunyaŋu godoo. Eƒe nɔnɔme naamɔ amesiame si ateŋu azã ''internet'' kple ''browserwo'' ŋudɔ be wòatrɔ nusiwo le eme. Ne nɔ nyanyame nawò be menye nusianu si le afisia me nunyaladeŋgɔwo kple agbalẽnyalagãwo to be wole eme vavã o. Esia melegbɔgblɔm be wòmakpɔ nuveviewo kple nunya vavã le ''Wikipiɖia'' la dzi o; zigeɖe la, wòakpɔe. Gake '''''Wikipiɖia''''' ma ateŋu ado ŋugbe nawò be nusianu si le afisia le eme vavã o. Ɣeaɖewoɣi la, nuŋɔŋlɔa ɖewo ƒe tatawo woatrɔ medidi o, elabena ameaɖe alo nubaɖawɔla ɖe wɔ tɔtrɔa ɖe si mesɔ kple nunyalawo kple agbãlenyalawo le xexeame katã ƒe susuwo o. === Nuwo me toto === Míele asitrɔm le alesi míatia alo míade dzesi nuŋɔŋlɔwo ƒe tata siwo ŋu ŋugbe le. Míaƒe nuŋlɔlawo zãna dɔwɔnu tɔxea ɖewo abe [[Special:Recentchanges|Tɔtrɔ yeyewo]] kple [[Special:Newpages|Axa yeyewo]] tsɔ nɔ ŋkulem ɖe nuyeyewo kple tɔtrɔ yeyeawo ŋu. Habɔbɔa ɖeke meli si toa ''Wikipiɖia'' la me o; togbɔ be nuxlẽla geɖewo wɔna ɖɔɖɔɖowo alo wotoa nuaɖewo me hã abe [[Wikipedia:Peer review|''peer review'']], sea ɖeke meli si na dɔ sia wɔwɔ o. Nuŋɔŋlɔ siwo wotia kpɔ le wome toto megbe hã abe [[Wikipedia:Featured articles|''featured article'']] woteŋu trɔna emegbe elabena ameaɖe vayi wɔ tɔtrɔ vɔ̃ɖia ɖe hafi nevale exlem. ::'''Wòmateŋu abu fɔ nuŋlɔla, kpeɖeŋutɔ, amesi na nu, dɔdzikpɔla, sysɔp kple amesiwo katã do ƒome kple ''Wikipiɖia'' wodometɔa ɖeke ɖe numanomeea ɖe si le afisia ŋu lo alo le wòŋutɔ ƒe emenuwo zãza ŋuti o.''' === Gɔmesesea ɖeke meli o; mɔɖeɖe tɔxe === Taflatse, eme nekɔ na amesiame bena nusiwo katã woŋlɔ ɖe afisia li fãa na amewokatã, eye ŋugbedodoa ɖeke mele wò kpakple afisia ƒe aƒetɔwo kple ezãlawo, amesiwo ƒe mɔwo dzi nuŋɔŋlawo le, ''Wikipiɖia'' la me nuŋlŋlawo ɖesiaɖe, dɔdzikpɔlawo, sysɔpwo alo amebuba ɖeke si do ƒome kple dɔ sia alo eƒe ƒomedodowo o. Mɔɖeɖea ɖe li be na tsɔ nusianu fãa tso afisia; Esia me fia be gɔmesesea ɖeke li le ''Wikipiɖia'' kple eƒe dɔwɔlawo kple ezãlawo kpakple wò dome o. '''Mɔɖeɖe alo gɔmesesea ɖeke mele wò kple ''Wikipiɖia'' dome''' na nyasiawo zãza alo wotɔtrɔ si mele [[GNU Free Documentation License]] (GFDL) mɔɖeɖewo nu o; Ne ameaɖe wɔ tɔtrɔa ɖe le nusiwo neŋlɔ ŋu le ''Wikipiɖia'' dzi alo woɖe eƒe akpa ɖe la, wòmekpɔ mɔ abu fɔ ''Wikipiɖia'' alo eƒe ƒomedodoa ɖeke o. === Trademarks /(Dzesi tɔxewo) === Dzesi tɔxe (abe ''trademarks, service marks, collective marks, design rights, personality rights'') siwo dze le Wikipiɖia la me la nye nutɔwo ŋutɔ tɔ. Woƒe zãzã le afisia mefia be mɔ li na wo ŋudɔ wɔwɔ le goa ɖeke me si to vovo na esiwo woɖe mɔ na le GFDL mɔɖeɖewo te o. Ne wome gblɔe fitaa o la, ekema ƒomedodoa ɖeke mele Wikipiɖia kple Wikimedia kpakple dzesitɔa ɖeke o eyata Wikipiɖia mateŋu aɖe mɔ na ameaɖeke be wòazã nusiwo nutɔwo meɖe mɔ na o la. ''Ne ezã nusiawo la, ele ɖokuiwò si, eye ne nyaɖe tso ezãzã me la, wò ɖeka ƒe agba ye.'' === Sesiwo te Wikipiɖia le === Ɖewomahĩ ''Wikipiɖia'' menuwo ɖeɖefia alo woŋɔŋlɔ ada se dzi le dukɔ alo afisi wòle la me. ''Wikipiɖia'' dɔwo katã le mɔwo dzi le [[Florida]] le [[United States of America]] eye wozãa wo le afima ƒe sewo nu. Se siwo le wòƒe dukɔme ƒe mɔɖeɖewo na nusiwo wòateŋu agblɔ alo nusiwo wòateŋu ama na amewo ateŋu ato vovo tso esiawo gbɔ. ''Wikipiɖia'' me doa ŋuse ameaɖeke be wòa da wo de sewo dzi o eyata ne eda se siawo dzi la, wò ɖeka woa bu fɔe. === Afisia meye aɖaŋuɖoƒe o === Ne ehiã aɖaŋu na nutɔxea ɖe (le kpɔɖeŋu me, dɔyɔyɔ, sewo, ganyawo) me la, di amesi wɔa dɔ le numa ŋuti. Kpɔ [[Wikipedia:Risk disclaimer]], [[Wikipedia:Medical disclaimer]], and [[Wikipedia:Legal disclaimer]] hã. Mieda akpe nawo bena ne gbɔdzi ɖi xlẽ nusiwo le afisia eye míe xɔese be ''Wikipiɖia'' la zãzã adze ŋuwo. ==Kpɔɖeŋu le nunyagbãle bubuwo ƒe ''"disclaimer-wo"'' ŋu== Togbɔ be wona agbãlenyalawo kple nusrɔ̃ladeŋgɔwo to nunyagbãle bubwo me hã, yawo hã medo ŋugbe be nusianu le eme vavã o. * [http://corporate.britannica.com/termsofuse.html britannica.com disclaimer] la (tso afisi ''[[Encyclopædia Britannica]]'' la le): *:"YOUR USE OF BRITANNICA.COM IS AT YOUR SOLE RISK." (''Iŋlisigbe'') *[http://privacy.msn.com/tou/ MSN.com disclaimer] la (tso afisi Microsoft ƒe [[Encarta|Encarta Encyclopedia]] la le) *: "...AND THE ENTIRE RISK AS TO SATISFACTORY QUALITY, PERFORMANCE, ACCURACY, AND EFFORT IS WITH YOU." (''Iŋlisigbe'') *[http://www.Bartleby.com/sv/terms.html bartleby.com disclaimer] la (tso afisi ''[[Columbia Encyclopedia]]'' la le) *: "YOU EXPRESSLY AGREE THAT USE OF THE SERVICE IS AT YOUR SOLE RISK." (''Iŋlisigbe'') [[de:Wikipedia:Impressum#Haftungsausschluss]] [[eu:Wikipedia:Erantzukizunen mugaketa orokorra]] [[pt:Wikipedia:Aviso Geral]]

'''Dzigbe ŋkɔ''' enye ŋkɔ si wotsɔna na amewo si fiaa ŋkeke si dzi woƒe dzigbe dze. Ŋkɔ siawo tsɔtsɔ bɔ ɖe [[Bluɔwo]] kple [[Eʋeawo]] dome le [[Ghana]]. Ekaka yi [[Jamaica]] hãa le [[Amerika]] nutowome. Ŋkɔawo to vovo na [[ŋutsu]]wo kple [[nyɔnu]]wo.
[[Robert Sutherland Rattray]] ("Captain R.S.Rattray") srɔ̃nu geɖe le [[Asanteawo]] ŋu vayi eye wògblɔ be "Dzigbe ŋkɔ le Asante vidzidzi ɖesiaɖe si". Wofia ŋkɔ siawo le Eʋegbe kple Blugbe me le afii.

[[Eʋeawo]] tsɔ na '''''vi''''' alo '''''ga''''' kpe na ɖe dzigbe ŋkɔ siawo nu he tsɔ na doa dzesi amea ƒe nɔnɔme. Le kpɔɖeŋu me, '''''Kɔku''''' kple '''''vi''''' zu na '''''Kɔkuvi''''' eye '''''Yao''''' kple '''''ga''''' zu na '''''Yaoga''''' ==Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe== *[[:en:Day name|Dzigbeŋkɔ le Iŋlisi Wikipiɖia dzi]]

[[File:Les Très Riches Heures du duc de Berry octobre.jpg|thumb|right|Kele tso ''Très Riches Heures du Duc de Berry'' la me.]] '''Kele''' (alo '''Ɔktober''') enye ɣleti ewolia le [[Gregoria ɣletigbalẽ]]a me. Ŋkeke 31 ye le ɣletia me.
Le Latingbe me la, ''octo'' gɔme enye "enyi" si fia be Ɔktober nye ɣleti enyilia le Romatɔwo ƒe ɣletigbalẽ me.
== Ŋkeke tɔxewo le Kele me == * [[Akpedada (Canada)|Thanksgiving]] ([[Canada]]) - Dzoɖa evelia le Kele me. * [[Dukɔ zã]] ([[China, People's Republic of]]) - Kele 1 * [[Ɖeviwo ƒe agbãlewo|Ɖeviwo ƒe agbãle kɔsiɖa]] le ([[England]]) - Kɔsiɖa gbãtɔ le Kele me. * Portugal Republik la ɖoɖo - Kele 5 * Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke le [[Croatia]]-Kele 8 * [[Columbus Day]] (Most of [[United States]]) - Dzoɖa evelia le Kele me. * [[Apple Day]] - Kele 21 * [[United Nations Day]] - Kele 24 * Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke le St. Vincent & the Grenadines - Kele 27 * Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke le Nigeria- Kele 1 * Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke le the Republic Of Cyprus [Kele 1 * Ɖokuisinɔnɔ Ŋkeke le Turkmenistan - Kele 27
== Nu bubuwo == * Kele ƒe kpe xɔasi enye'' opal'' or ''tourmaline''. * Kele ƒe seƒoƒo enye ''calendula'' or ''cosmos''. * Woyɔna Kele (alo Ɔktober) be Ɔktober dzẽ elabena ɣleti sia me zitɔtɔ dze egɔme le [[Russia]]. Le Gregoria ɣletigbãlea nu la, Adeɛmekpɔxe enye ɣleti si me nuawo katã dzɔ. * Kele kple Siamlɔm enye ɣleti siwo me vidzidziwo sɔgbɔ wu.

'''Emmanuel Kɔsi Kotoka''' ([[Kele 26]] [[1926]] - [[Afɔfiɛ 17]] [[1967]]) nye asrafo si nɔ [[National Liberation Council]] dziɖuɖu si nɔ zia dzi tso [[Dzodze 24]] [[1966]]. Dziɖuɖu siae ɖe dukplɔla [[Kwame Nkrumah]] le [[Ghana]] dukɔ zia dzi.
==Kotoka ƒe ɖevime== Wodzi Kotoka le Alakple<ref name="ghanaweb">[http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/people/pop-up.php?ID=120 GhanaWeb.com]</ref> si nye Keta dukɔ ɖeka le [[Vɔlta nutome]] le Ghana. Ede suku le Alakple Roman Catholic Suku. Emegbe la, eyi eƒe suku dede dzi le Anloga Senior School tso ƒe 1941 me.<ref name="ghanaweb"/> Esi wòde suku vɔ la, eɖo be yea srɔ̃ dɔ gake emegbe la, evaye ŋlɔ ŋkɔ kple asrafowo.
==Asrafo dɔwɔwɔ== Le Siamlɔm 1947 me la, Kotoka dze asrafodɔ sɔsrɔ̃ gɔme le Gold Coast Regiment ƒe asrafo suku le [[Teshie]] le [[Gẽ]]. Dɔa sɔsrɔ̃ tsɔ afɔ ne. Le ƒe 1952 me la, enɔ Afrika asrafow dɔmetɔwo siwo woɖo ɖe Eaton Hall, si nye asrafo suku de ŋgɔ ɖeka le [[United Kingdom]] (Britannia) dukɔa me. Le ƒe 1954 me la, woɖoe leftenant le Ghana asrafowo me, eye wòdze dɔwɔwɔ gɔme kple Britannia asrafowo le [[Rhine]] si le Dzama dukɔa me.<ref name="Kraus">[http://home.comcast.net/~amaah/writings/ghana-without-nkrumah-men-in-charge.html Africa Report - John Kraus]</ref>
Esi wògbɔ va Gold Coast la, woɖoe ''Platoon Commander'' le ''Second Gold Coast Regiment of Infantry'' la me. Le ƒe [[1959]] me la, ezu asrafo mega si woyɔna be Captain. Le ƒe ma me ke la, woɖoe Major. Le ƒe 1960 me la, evaye de Asrafo megawo suku de ŋgɔ ɖeka le [[Westminster]] le [[Inglis]] nyigbaa dzi.
Le ƒe 1960 me la, Kotoka nye asrafo mega wodometɔ ɖeka le Ghana asrafowo si woɖo ɖe Congo. Woyi vaye le vu le Leopoldville (si nye [[Kinshasa]] egbe la) kple [[Xexeme Dukɔ Ƒoƒuawo]] asrafowo le afima.<ref>[http://www.black-history-month.co.uk/articles/nkrumah.html Wellplaced Consultancy]</ref> Kotoka do kalẽ ŋutɔ le dɔ sia gbe eye Ghana dukɔa na dzesi tɔxee si nye ''Ghana Service Order for Exceptional Bravery for Distinguished Service in the Congo'' le ƒe 1963 me.<ref name="ghanaweb"/>
Emegbe la, Kotoka va zu kplɔla na Ghana asrafowo katã le Ghana ƒe dzigbe kpa dzi si nye ''Second Infantry Brigade'' (si woyɔna be Northern Command egbe) le Kumasi.<ref name="Kraus"/>
==Ghana dukɔ kplɔkplɔ== Kotoka nɔ ŋgɔ na asrafowo si ɣlẽ Ghana dziɖuɖua tso Nkrumah ƒe [[Convention People's Party]] dziɖuɖua dzi.
<!-- ****************Need to translate this section********************* ==Politics== In 1965, the then [[Lieutenant-Colonel]] Kotoka was transferred to Kumasi where he met and became friends with then [[Akwasi Afrifa|Major Akwasi Amankwa Afrifa]], an officer in the Second Brigade of the Ghana army.<ref name="ghanaweb"/> The two are generally credited with being among the key conspirators behind the first bloody coup d'état in Ghana on [[February 24]], [[1966]] which brought an end to the first republic. They codenamed it "Operation Cold Chop".<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ghana.gov.gh/NRC/Vol%204%20Chpt%201%20com.sec.rep.pdf |title=The Security Services |accessdate=2007-06-11 |work=National Reconciliation Commission Report Volume 4 Chapter 1|format=pdf |pages=page24 |date=October 2004 |publisher=Ghana government}}</ref> It was Kotoka who announced the coup to the nation early that morning from the Broadcasting House of the Ghana Broadcasting Corporation, the official radio station in Ghana. The [[Central Intelligence Agency]] appears to have been aware about the plotting of the coup at least a year ahead.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/www/about_state/history/vol_xxiv/y.html |title=253. Memorandum From Robert W. Komer of the National Security Council Staff to the President's Special Assistant for National Security Affairs (Bundy)/1/ |accessdate=2007-03-19 |year=1999 |work=FOREIGN RELATIONS OF THE UNITED STATES 1964-1968, Volume XXIV Africa |publisher=Department of State, USA |quote="The plotters are keeping us briefed," .... "and the State Department thinks we're more on the inside than the British. While we're not directly involved (I'm told), we and other Western countries (including France) have been helping to set up the situation by ignoring Nkrumah's pleas for economic aid. All in all, it looks good."}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.seeingblack.com/x060702/nkrumah.shtml |title=Documents Expose U.S. Role in Nkrumah Overthrow |accessdate=2007-03-19 |author=Paul Lee |date=June 7, 2002 |publisher=SeeingBlack.com}}</ref> Kotoka was promoted [[Major General]] and became a member of the ruling National Liberation Council and also the Commissioner for [[Health|Ministry of Health]] as well as [[General Officer Commanding]] the Ghana Armed Forces. --> ==Eƒe ku== Le [[Afɔfiɛ 17]] dzi le ƒe [[1967]] me la, asrafo aɖewo tso ɖe NLC dziɖuɖua ŋu. Woɖo be yewoa xɔ dziɖuɖua kple sesɛ̃. Wonɔ dɔwɔm kple Ghana asrafowo si nɔ ''Mortar Regiment'' le [[Ho]], si nye Vɔlta nutome dugã. Le hoʋiʋli si dzɔ me la, asrafoawo wodometɔ ɖeka, si nye Moses Yeboah la, wu Kotoka. Kotoka ƒe asrafowo ƒe alɔ fɔ dzi le hoʋiʋlia ƒe nuwuwu, eye wo drɔ ʋɔnu na Yeboah kple eƒe ahatiwo. Wobu fɔ Yeboah kple xɔ̃awɔ̃o eye wo wu wo.<ref>[http://lcweb2.loc.gov/cgi-bin/query/r?frd/cstdy:@field(DOCID+gh0147) Library of Congress Country Studies - Ghana: The Military and the Government]</ref>
Wome Kotoka ƒe tata heda ɖe afisi wofɔ Kotoka ƒe kukua le. Ghana dukɔa ƒe ayameʋu dzeƒe gã tɔwu le afisia, eye wotrɔ ŋkɔaɔ zu [[Kotoka International Airport]] hetsɔ ɖo ŋku Kotoka dzi.
==Nya siawo ƒe tsoƒe== <References/>

Wotsɔna ŋkeke sia ɖoa ŋku nusiwo ŋu woŋlɔnu daɖi le [[Biblia]] alo Ŋɔŋlɔ Kɔkɔe la ƒe Nubabla yeye la me. Enye Yehowa Ðasefowo ƒe didi be nàdze si yewo nyuie wu. Ðewohĩ wonye wò aƒelikawo kple dɔwɔhatiwo alo èdoa go wo le gbesiagbedɔwɔna bubuwo me. Ðewohĩ èkpɔa wo le ablɔwo dzi wonɔa woƒe magazinewo nam amesiwo va yina. Alo ɖewohĩ èƒo nu kpli wo kpuie le wò ʋɔtru nu kpɔ.
Le nyateƒe me la, Yehowa Ðasefowo tsɔ ɖe le wò kple wò nyonyo me. Wodi be yewoadze xɔ̃ wò ahagblɔ nya geɖe na wò tso wo ɖokui, woƒe dzixɔsewo, woƒe habɔbɔa, kple nusi nye woƒe susu le amewo kple xexe si me mí katã míele ŋu. Esia tae wota agbalẽ gbadza sia na wò ɖo.
Yehowa Ðasefowo le abe ame bubu ɖesiaɖe ene le go geɖe me. Kuxiwo nɔa woawo hã ŋu—le ganya, ŋutilã me, kple seselelãme gome. Wowɔa vodada ɣeaɖewoɣi, elabena womede blibo o, wometso gbɔgbɔ me, alo nye vovodadamanɔŋutɔwo o. Gake wodzea agbagba be yewoasrɔ̃ nu tso yewoƒe nuteƒekpɔkpɔwo me eye wosrɔ̃a Biblia vevie tsɔ wɔa ɖɔɖɔɖo siwo hiã. Woɖe adzɔgbe na Mawu be yewoawɔ eƒe lɔlɔ̃nu, eye wotsɔa wo ɖokui nana be yewoawɔ adzɔgbeɖeɖe sia dzi. Wodia Mawu ƒe Nya kple eƒe gbɔgbɔ kɔkɔe ƒe mɔfiafia le woƒe dɔwɔnawo katã me.
== Woɖe adzɔgbe na Mawu be yewoawɔ eƒe lɔlɔ̃nu == Wobunɛ nu vevii be yewoatu yewoƒe dzixɔsewo ɖe Biblia dzi ke menye ɖe amegbetɔ ƒe nususukpɔ alo hakplɔɖoɖo dzrowo ko dzi o. Wosena le wo ɖokui me abe apostolo Paulo ene esime gbɔgbɔ ʋãe wògblɔ be: “Mawu nye nyateƒetɔ, ke amesiame aʋatsokalae.” (Romatɔwo 3:4, Eʋegbe Biblia*) Le nufiafia siwo wogblɔ be enye Biblia me nyateƒe gome la, Ðasefowo léa nusi Beroiatɔwo wɔ esime apostolo Paulo ɖe gbeƒã na wo la me ɖe asi sesĩe: “Woxɔ nya la kple dzi faa, eye wole ŋɔŋlɔawo me dzrom gbesiagbe be, nusiawo le eme hã.” (Dɔwɔwɔwo 17:11) Yehowa Ðasefowo xɔe se be ele be woatsɔ Ŋɔŋlɔ siwo tso gbɔgbɔ me la ado mawusubɔsubɔ me nufiafiawo katã kpɔ alea, eɖanye woa ŋutɔwo ƒe nufiafia loo alo ame bubu tɔ o. Wokpe wò—wole dzi dem ƒo na wò—be nàwɔ esia le dzeɖoɖo kpli wo me.
== Woxɔe se be Biblia nye Mawu ƒe Nya == Míate ŋu akpɔe le esia me be Yehowa Ðasefowo xɔ Biblia dzi se be enye Mawu ƒe Nya. Wobua eƒe agbalẽ 66-awo be wotso gbɔgbɔ me eye wo me nudzɔdzɔwo nye blemaŋutinya ŋutɔŋutɔwo. Woyɔa Nubabla Yeye si ame geɖe nya la be Kristotɔwo ƒe Hela Ŋɔŋlɔawo, eye woyɔa Nubabla Xoxoa be Hebri Ŋɔŋlɔawo. Wozãa evea, Hela kple Hebri Ŋɔŋlɔawo siaa, eye wobua wo me nyaawo ɖe alesi wogblɔ woe nu pɛpɛpɛ negbe teƒe siwo nyagbɔgblɔa alo nɔnɔme si me wogblɔe le na wòdze ƒã be wonye kpɔɖeŋunyagbɔgblɔ alo tsi tre ɖi na nu bubu aɖe ko. Wose egɔme be Biblia me nyagblɔɖi geɖe va eme, bubuwo le eme vam, eye bubuwo agava eme le etsɔme.
== Woɖe ŋkɔ == Yehowa Ðasefowoa? Ẽ, nenemae woyɔa wo ɖokuii. Enye nɔnɔmefiaŋkɔ si fia be woɖia ɖase le Yehowa, eƒe Mawunyenye, kple eƒe tameɖoɖowo ŋu. “Mawu,” “Aƒetɔ,” kple “Wɔla”—siwo le abe “Dukplɔla,” “Fia,” kple “Aʋafia” ene—nye dzesideŋkɔwo eye woate ŋu azã wo na ame vovovo geɖe. Gake “Yehowa” ya nye ŋkɔ tɔxɛ eye Mawu ŋusẽkatãtɔ kple xexeme Wɔla lae wozãnɛ na. Woɖe esia fia le Psalmo 83:19 be: “Ne woadze sii be, ŋkɔwòe nye YEHOWA, eye wò ɖeɖe koe ɖo kpo ɖe anyigba blibo la dzi!”
== Mawu ŋutɔ ƒe ŋkɔ le blema Hebrigbe me == Ŋkɔ Yehowa (alo Yahweh, abe alesi Roma Katoliko ƒe Jerusalem Bible kple agbalẽnyala aɖewo yɔnɛ ene la) dze zi gbɔ zi 7,000 le Hebri Ŋɔŋlɔawo me. Womedee Biblia akpa gãtɔ me alea o, ke boŋ wotsɔ “Mawu” alo “Aƒetɔ” ɖo eteƒe. Gake le Biblia siawo me gɔ̃ hã la, woate ŋu akpɔ afisi wozã Yehowa le le Hebrigbe me kpukpuiawo me elabena ŋɔŋlɔdzesigãwo ƒe lolotɔwo kple suetɔwoe wotsɔ ŋlɔa nya siwo wotsɔ ɖo ŋkɔa teƒee, si nye: MAWU kple AƑETƆ. Egbegbe gɔmeɖeɖe geɖe zã ŋkɔ Yehowa alo Yahweh. Eyata Yesaya 42:8 xlẽ le Eʋegbe Biblia me be, “Nyee nye Yehowa, ŋkɔnyee.”
== Ŋkɔa do ƒome kple ʋɔnudrɔ̃ƒe nudzɔdzɔ == Ŋɔŋlɔawo me nya si me Yehowa Ðasefowo ɖe woƒe ŋkɔ tsoe la le Yesaya ta 43 lia. Le afima la, woɖɔ xexeame ƒe nɔnɔme abe nusi le edzi yim le ʋɔnudrɔ̃ƒe ene: Wogblɔ na dukɔwo ƒe mawuwo be woakplɔ woƒe ɖasefowo vɛ ne woava ɖo kpe edzi ne woƒe nya dzɔ alo be woase ɖasefo siwo le Yehowa ƒe akpa dzi ƒe nya ale be woalɔ̃ ɖe nyateƒea dzi. Afimae Yehowa gblɔ na eƒe amewo le be: “Miawoe nye nye ɖasefowo kple nye dɔla, si metia, ne mianyae, miaxɔ dzinye ase, eye miadze sii be, nyee. Womewɔ mawu aɖeke do ŋgɔ nam o, eye ɖeke mado megbe nam o. Nyee nye Yehowa, eye xɔnametɔ aɖeke meli kpe ɖe ŋunye o.”—Yesaya 43:10, 11.
Ðasefowo nɔ Yehowa Mawu si le anyigba dzi ƒe akpe geɖe hafi wova dzi Yesu. Esi Hebritɔwo ta 11 yɔ xɔsetɔ siawo dometɔ aɖewo ƒe ŋkɔ vɔ la, Hebritɔwo 12:1 gblɔ be: “Eyata míawo hã, esi ɖaseɖilawo ƒe alilikpo gã ŋutɔ ƒo xlã mí la, mina míaɖe nu kpekpe sia nu kpekpe kple nuvɔ̃, si ɖea to ɖe mí la ɖa, eye mina míatsɔ dzidodo anɔ dudimekeke, si woɖo na mí la dzi.” Yesu gblɔ le Pontio Pilato ŋkume be: “Esia ta wodzim ɖo, eye esia ta meva xexeame ɖo, bena maɖi ɖase na nyateƒe la.” Woyɔe be “ɖaseɖila nuteƒewɔla kple nyateƒetɔ.” (Yohanes 18:37; Nyaɖeɖefia 3:14) Yesu gblɔ na eƒe nusrɔ̃lawo be: “Miaxɔ [gbɔgbɔ] kɔkɔe, si le mia dzi va ge la, ƒe ŋusẽ, eye mianye nye ɖaseɖilawo le Yerusalem kple Yudea katã kple Samaria, eye vaseɖe anyigba ƒe seƒe ke.”—Dɔwɔwɔwo 1:8.
== Ðasefo siwo ade 7,700,000 le dukɔ 239 kple edzivɔ me == Eyata amesiwo ade 7,782,346 siwo le Yehowa ƒe Fiaɖuƒe si le Kristo Yesu si me ŋuti nyanyuia gblɔm le dukɔ siwo ade 236 me la kpɔe be esɔ be yewoayɔ yewo ɖokui be Yehowa Ðasefowo (2012).
* [http://www.jw.org/ee/ Yehowa Ɖasefowo]

== Marking quality articles == This is a template to promote Wikipedia's featured articles by marking them subtly with little stars ([[Image:Monobook-bullet-star.png]]) nearby the interlanguage links. Note: If you also have a category "featured articles", your featured articles are already starred on the other Wikipedias as well with this {{Link FA|ee}} system! === How to enable this? === Unfortunately, no improvements at all are made towards the interwiki linking system of the MediaWiki software. [[File:Coat of arms of Senegal.svg|right|120px]] [[File:Flag of Senegal.svg|right|200px]] [[File:LocationSenegal.svg|right|200px]] [[File:Senegal Regions.png|thumbnail|left|250px|Regions of Senegal]] '''Senegal''' nye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Ele [[Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe]] lɔƒo. Senegal do liƒo kple [[Mauritania]] le eƒe dzigbe kpa dzi, [[Mali]] le eƒe ɣedzeƒe kpa dzi, eye [[Guinea]] kple [[Guinea-Bissau]] le eƒe anyigbe lɔƒo. Aƒu si woyɔna be [[{{SIL|Atlantic Ocean}}]] la le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo. Senegal ƒoxlã [[Gambia]] dukɔa le eƒe axa etɔ̃ dzi. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 11,658,000 lɔƒo.
Senegal dukɔa xɔ ɖokuisinɔnɔ tso [[France]] dukɔ ƒe dziɖuɖu la te le [[Dasiamime]] ƒe ŋkeke 20 lia dzi le ƒe 1960 me. Senega ƒe dugã enye [[Dakar]]. Senegal ƒe dukplɔla enye [[Abdoulaye Wade]]. Ele dziɖum tso [[Afɔfiɛ]] ƒe ŋkeke gbãtɔ dzi, le ƒe 2000 me.
{{Afrika dukɔwo}}

[[File:LocationMali.svg|right|180px]] [[File:Flag of Mali.svg|right|180px]]
Mali nye [[Afrika]] dukɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Dukɔ ade ko ye lolo wui le Afrika godoo. Mali do liƒo kple [[Algeria]] le dzigbe lɔƒo, [[Niger]] le eƒe ɣedzeƒe lɔƒo, [[Burkina Faso]] kple [[Côte d'Ivoire]] le eƒe anyigbe, [[Guinea]], [[Senegal]] kple [[Mauritania]] le eƒe ɣetoɖoƒe kpa dzi. Eƒe dukɔmenɔlawo ƒe xexlẽme ɖo 11,995,402 lɔƒo.
Le blema ŋɔli la, dukɔ etɔ̃ siwo xɔ ŋkɔ ŋtɔ nɔ afisi Mali le egbe la. Woawo wonye [[Ghana dukɔ]], [[Mali dukɔ]] kple [[Sɔngai dukɔ]]. Ghana dukɔ kple Sɔngai dukɔ womegalee fifia o.
{{Afrika dukɔwo}}

[[File:Rembrandt Harmensz. van Rijn 035.jpg|thumbnail|Abraham kple Isak]] '''Abraham''' nye amesi ŋu woŋlɔ nu le le [[Mose I|Mose ƒe agbalẽ gbãtɔ]] me le [[Biblia]]a me. Wo ga ŋlɔ nu le eya ke ŋuti le [[Koran]] la hã me. Kristotɔwo kple Mohammed subɔlawo katã bu nae abe Israel viwo, Ishamel viwo kple Edom viwo katã wo fofo. Eya dzi Yuda subɔsubɔ kple Kristo subɔsubɔ to.
Abraham nye [[Tarax]] vi, eye wònye [[Naxor]] ƒe tɔgbeyɔvi. Abraham nɔviwo wonye [[Naxor]] kple [[Haran]]. Bibla gblɔ bena Mawu kplɔ Abraham tso [[Mesopotamia]] vayi [[Kanaan]] nyigba dzi. Afima Mawu bla nu kple Abraham le. Tso ema dzi la, Abraham subɔ Mawu dzaa ko abe Mawu ene. Mawu ga do ŋugbe na Abraham hã bena eƒe dzidzimeviwo woadzi xexlẽmanɔmee. Abraham nɔ agbe tso AM 1948–2123 (1812 BCE vaseɖe 1637 BCE).
Yudatɔwo yɔna Abraham be Avraham, Avinu, alo "Abraham, mía Fofo". Mawu do ŋugbe na Abraham bena woayra amegbetɔwo katã to eƒe dzidziemviwo dzi. (Mose I 12:3). Kristotɔwo kpɔ [[Yesu Kristo]] abe ŋugbe si Mawu na Abraham. Mohammed subɔlawo xɔ edzi se bena Mohammed nye [[Ismael]], ŋutsuvi si [[Hagar]] dzi na Abraham ƒe dzidzimeviwo dometɔ ɖeka.
{{Adam vayi Dawid}}

'''Tarax''', si gɔme enye tsatsala la, enye [[Abraham]] fofo le [[Biblia]] me.
== Amea == === Biblia === Le [[Mose I|Mose ƒe agbalẽ gbãtɔ]] me la, Tarax nye [[Naxor]] viŋutsu, eye eya hã nye [[Serug]] viŋutsu. Serug fofo nye [[Regu]], si fofo enye [[Peleg]], si fofo nye [[Eber]], si fofo nye [[Selax]], si fofo nye [[Arpaxsad]], si fofo nye [[Sem]], si nye [[Noa]] viŋutsu tsitsi tɔ.<ref>Mose I 11:10-26</ref>
Biblia gblɔ be Tarax dzi viŋutsu etɔ̃. Yawo enye [[Abram]], [[Naxor]] kple [[Xaran]]. Le Mose I ta 20:12 me la, [[Sara]], si nye Abraham srɔ̃ nye nɔvia hã, elabena woameve nye [[Terax]] viwo gake wo nɔwo to vovo. Wo de enye [[Ur]] le [[Kaldea]] nyigba dzi. Tarax vi Xaran tre kuku na tɔa le Ur. Xaran dzi [[Lot]] hafi wò ku. Naxor tso aƒe ɖe Xaran, si le Ur mɔ dzi. Tarax ʋu tso Ur kple via Abraham kple eƒe tɔgbeyɔviŋutsu Lot. Woƒe ɖoɖo enye be yewoayi [[Kanaan]] gake wodze Xaran eye Terax ku le afima.<ref>Mose I 11:24-32</ref> Le eƒe ku megbe la, Abram kple eƒe ƒometɔwo ʋu tso Xaran. <ref>Dɔwɔwɔwo 7:4</ref> Biblia gblɔ bena Tarax nye trɔ̃subɔɔla.<ref>Yosua 24:2</ref>
== Teƒe == Tarax enye teƒe si Israeltɔwo tɔ ɖa le ɣeyiɣi sime wonɔ sisim tso [[Egyipte]].
== Nyasiawo ƒe tsoƒe == <references/>

[[File:Grand aulacode male.jpg|thumb|Nukpui tsu si wo le nyinyim le Gabon]] '''Nukpui''' alo ( Latin ŋkɔ: ''Thryonomys swinderianus'') enye gbeme lã si bɔ le [[Afrika]]. Nukpuiwo lɔ̃na tsi gbɔ nɔnɔ. Wotsana le agblewo me hã. Tsitsiawo ƒe didime gbɔa "feet" eve dzi le goɖewo me.
Eƒe towo kple ŋɔtiwo le takpo eye eƒe fũwo sẽ. Woƒe megbe fɔwo melolo abe ŋgɔgbe tɔwo o. Nukpuiwo tsana le ha alo ƒome suewo me eye atsu ɖeka nɔa ha ɖesiaɖe nu. Nukpuiwo lɔ̃a zãme nɔnɔ. Ɣeaɖewo ɣii hã, wonɔna tome. Woteŋu nɔa agbe ƒe ene sɔ̃. Ne nu aɖe dovɔ̃vɔ wo la, wosina yea tsi me. Gbe enye woƒe nuɖuɖu gãtɔ gake wo lɔ̃na agble me nukuwo hã ɖuɖu eyata wogblena nukuwo ŋutɔ na agbledelawo.
Le [[Ghana]] kple Afrika ƒe ɣetoɖoƒe lɔƒo la, woyɔnae be ''grasscutter''. Le Afrika ƒe akpa geɖewo me la, nukpuiwo nye lã si amewo ɖua ŋutɔ. Le esia ta la, wodze nukpuiwo nyim na dzadzra le teƒewo geɖe.
== Kpɔɖeŋuwo == * Matthews, Jaman. "The Value of Grasscutters," ''World Ark'', (Dzove-Dzodze, 2008), pp. 23-24.(''Nukpuiwo ƒe asixɔxɔ'' le Iŋglisigbe)
== Nuxexlẽ bubuwo == * [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/4864714.stm BBC nuŋɔŋlɔ le nukpuiwo ŋu le Ghana] (Iŋglisigbe)

'''Sylvanus Epiphanio Olympio''' (1902 - 1963). enye [[Togo dukplɔlawo]] ƒe gbātɔ.
== Dumèdɔ wɔwɔ == Aƒetɔ Olympio nye Togo ƒe dudɔnunɔla gbātɔ tso ƒe 1958 vaseɖe ƒe 1961 me. Le ɣeyiɣi siawo me la, wo ɖa àkɔ̃ nè ɣé wozu Togo dukplɔla tso ƒe 1961 vaseɖe 1963 me. Le Olympio ƒe dziɖuɖu ɣéɣíɣí wo mé la, Togo dze dumedɔ geɖe wo me.
== Nuwuwu == Le Dzove 13, 1963 ɖzi là, aƒéto Olympio ku le asrafowo ƒe dziɖudua trɔtrɔ me. Eƒe kukua ƒe wɔnao me mé kɔ̃ nyuie o. Le gbɔgblɔn sé ɖéo mè la, ɣémaɣi asrafo gɔmenotɔ̃ [[Gnassingbé Eyadéma]] ɣé nɔ ngɔ na tsitrétsiláwo. Lé gbɔgblɔn sé bubuwo mè la, asrafo Emmanuel Bodjollé ɣé nɔ ngɔ nawo.

[[File:FrancisAmenu.jpg|thumb|Osɔfo Francis Amenu]]
Osɔfo '''Francis Amenu''' enye Mɔɖeretɔ na [[Presbyteria Nyanyui Hame le Ghana]] la ƒe General Assembly.
==Sukudede== Osɔfo Amenu de Osɔfo suku le [[:en:Trinity Theological Seminary|Trinity College]] le [[Legon]] le [[Ghana]].<ref>[http://ttsem.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=category&sectionid=4&id=16&Itemid=44 Trinity Theological Seminary]</ref> Emegbe la, evayi de [[:en:Christian Theological Seminary|Christian Theological Seminary]], si le [[Indianapolis]] le [[United States]].<ref>[http://db.ghanaian-chronicle.com/thestory.asp?id=8112&title=EP%20Church%20ends%2067th%20Synod EP Church ends 67th Synod …with election of new Moderator and Clerk of General Assembly]</ref>
==Mawunya dɔwɔwɔ== Le Osɔfo Amenu ƒe ɖoɖo megbe la, ewɔ dɔ le nutome vovovowo. Enye osɔfo na Accra New Town hamea eye enɔ [[Ho]] hã. Hamea ɖoe ɖe ablotsi eye wò vayi nɔ [[London]] le [[United Kingdom]] alo Iŋglisiawo de abe Ghanatɔwo ƒe osɔfo ene.<ref>[http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/artikel.php?ID=38441 Ghana Home Page]</ref><ref>[http://www.bmcdirectory.org/agency_detail.php?uid=98 Black Majority Churches UK]</ref> Ewɔ dɔ kple [[United Reformed Church]] le afima<ref>[http://www.geocities.com/ccom_africa_forum/doc_files/030427Africa_Forum_Hamburg_FrancisAmenuDevotion.htm Churches Commission on Mission]</ref> tso ƒe 1999 me vaseɖe ƒe 2003 me. Egbɔ va Ghana le 2003 me eye wovayi ɖu osɔfo na Madina hamea.<ref>[http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/religion/artikel.php?ID=149050 Highest E.P Church decision-making body now General Assembly]</ref> Osɔfo Amenu nɔ nufiam le Trinity Theological Seminary le Legon<ref>[http://ttsem.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=category&sectionid=4&id=16&Itemid=44 Adjunct Lecturers, Trinity Theological Seminary]</ref> kpakple [[EP University]] yeyea si le [[Ho, Ghana|Ho]].<ref>[http://db.ghanaian-chronicle.com/thestory.asp?id=8112&title=EP%20Church%20ends%2067th%20Synod EP Church ends 67th Synod …with election of new Moderator and Clerk of General Assembly]</ref>
Woɖo Osɔfo Amenu Mɔɖeretɔ le hamea ƒe synod 67lia le Ho le Dasiamime le ƒe 2008 me.<ref>[http://news.myjoyonline.com/news/200808/19799.asp My Joy Online]</ref>
==Nuŋɔŋlɔ bubuwo== *[[Presbyteria Nyanyui Hame le Ghana]]

[[File:Huang Xianfan Graduation Photo.jpg|thumb|right|Huang Xianfan]] '''Huang Xianfan''' ([[Adeɛmekpɔxe]] 13, 1899 – [[Dzove]] 18, 1982) enye China xoxoawo ta tɔ ɖeka kpakple professor le University. <ref>[http://z.cctv.com/20100118/101326.shtml Xoxoawo ta tɔ ɖeka Huang Xianfan（Chinaweb-cctv.com）]</ref>
== Ɖevime kple sukudede == Wodzi Huang le Fusui le [[China]] le Adeɛmekpɔxe 13 le ƒe 1899 me.Eƒe dzilawo ƒe ŋkɔwo nye Huang Kechang kple Gan Lan. Ede suku le Fusui Suku. Emegbe la, eyi eƒe suku dede dzi le Nanning Normal School tso ƒe 1922 me.Huang de Beijing Normal University(1926-35) kple Tokyo Imperial University le [[Japan]](1935-37).<ref>[http://www.china.com.cn/aboutchina/zhuanti/zzfq08/2008-12/08/content_16914964.htm Professor Huang Xianfan （Chinaweb-china.com.cn）]</ref>
== Eƒe dɔwɔwɔ == Egbɔ va China le 1937 me. Tso Yanuar gbatɔ 1937 la, Huang dze dɔ gɔme abe nufiala le Nanning Senior School me. Tso Yanuar gbatɔ 1938 la, Huang nɔ nufiam le Guangxi University le Guilin(1938-41). Tso eƒe 1941 me vaseɖe 1942 me la, Huang nye professor le Sun Yatsen University le Guangdong kpakple tso ƒe 1943 me vaseɖe ƒe 1953 me nɔ professor le Guangxi University yeyea si le Guilin. Tso eƒe 1954 me vaseɖe 1982 me la, Huang nye professor le Guangxi Normal College le Guilin.<ref>[http://mz.china.com.cn/?action-viewnews-itemid-2300 Zhuang professor Huang Xianfan （Chinaweb-mz.china.com.cn）]</ref>
== Huang Xianfan ƒe agbalẽwo == * Outline of Chinese History（1932-1934） * Brief Introduction on Tang Dynasty（1936，1937，2009）ISBN 978-7-80762-492-9 * Save Nation Movement of Tai-Xue students in Song Dynasty（1936，1956，1965，1996，2009）ISBN 978-7-80762-492-9 * Brief History of the Guangxi Zhuang（1957） * No Slave Society in Chinese History（1981） * Nong Zhi Gao（1983） * General History of the Zhuang（1988）ISBN 7-5363-0422-6/K·13 * The Introduction on Chinese Ancient Books（2004）ISBN 7-5633-4743-7 * Wei Baqun Critical Biography（2008）ISBN 978-7-5633-7656-8<ref>[http://www.3hresearch.com/ShowArticle.asp?ArticleID=1864 Huang Xianfan ƒe agbalẽwo （Chinaweb.com）]</ref>
== Nuŋɔŋlɔ bubuwo == * [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Huang_group Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia - Huang Group] * [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zhuang_studies Eŋlisi Wikipiɖia - Zhuang suku] * [http://knol.google.com/k/bagui-school# Eŋlisi Bagui School]

/* Aƒlao ƒe nɔƒe */
revision.text:
'''Aƒlao''' alo '''Aflao''' enye du si le [[Ghana]] kpakple [[Togo]] woƒe liƒo dzi. Eŋlisiawo yɔna du sia be '[[:en:Aflao|Aflao]]'.
== Aƒlao ƒe nɔƒe == Aƒlao le Ketu South Distrikt me le [[Volta Region]] le Ghana. Distrikt la ƒe toxɔ du ye enye [[Denu]]. Togo nye dukɔ si le Ghana ƒe ɣedzeƒe kpa dzi eye [[Lome]] enye du si le Togo dukɔ me. [[Eʋegbe|Eʋeawo]] ƒe duwo demetɔ ɖekae nye Aƒlao. Aƒlao nye du mamlɛ tɔ sime na to hafi a geɖe [[Togo]] me.
== Kluvi si == Le blemaŋɔli la, Aƒlao nye kluvi si gãtɔ ɖeka. <ref>Dickson, K. B. "Trade Patterns in Ghana at the Beginning of the Eighteenth Century." Geographical Review 56.3 (1966): 417-431</ref> Asi gã aɖe gale Aƒlao fifia eye wodzrana nuvovowo le afima.<ref>[http://www.ghana-pedia.org/org/index.php?option=com_directory&listing=Aflao&page=viewListing&lid=228&Itemid=36 Aflao on Ghana-Pedia]</ref>
== Nyasiawo ƒe tsoƒe == {{Reflist}}

[[File:Ghana location map.svg|thumb|Ghana dukɔ]] '''Ʋegbe Kpalime''' enye dukɔ aɖe si le [[Ghana]] ƒe [[Vɔlta nutome]]. == Eƒe nɔƒe == Ʋegbe dukɔa teɖe [[Bame]] ŋu. Ele Ʋegbe ƒe dzigbe lɔƒo. [[Akrɔfu]] kple [[Aveŋui]] le eƒe anyigbe lɔƒo. [[Ho]], si nye Vɔlta nutome dugã did tso egbɔ abe kilometre 15 ene. == Dzɔdzɔme == Wo xɔese bena Kpaliawo ʋu va afisi wole fifia tso [[Ŋɔtsie]] le afisi [[Togo]] dukɔa le fifia. Wonɔ sisim na Tɔgbe Agɔkɔli, amesi nye Fiaga le Ŋɔtsie.[http://news.myjoyonline.com/news/200712/11168.asp MyJoyOnline] Wo ma ɖe akpa eve me. Akpa ɖeka zɔ yi anyigbe lɔƒɔ. Akpa evelia, sinye Ʋegbeawo, Kpevetɔwo kpakple Kleƒetɔwo vayi dze Vɔlta nutoame le afisi wo le fifia.[http://kledetf.over-blog.com/article-24602450.html ''Welcome to Klefe Dome] == Kpaliawo == Kpaliawo dzɔ tso [[Eʋeawo]] me eye Ʋegbe Kpalime enye Kpaleawo ƒe dukɔ ɖeka. Wodo ƒome kpakple Kpali du susueawo. Woaow enye Kpale, Todome, Tsatee, Hiama, Kaira, Toh kple Duga. Kpalime Duga enye woƒe du gã tɔ. Ʋegbe dukɔa ƒe azã vevietɔ enye [[Kpalikpakpaza]] siwo ɖuna ƒesiaa ƒe le ƒea ƒe nuwuwu lɔƒo. Woɖu azã sia zi gbãtɔ le 1997 me. Wotsɔna azã sia tsana Kpali dukɔawo dzi, eyata Kpali dukɔawo katã ɖunae le du ɖeka me.[http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/artikel.php?ID=2839 GhanaWeb.com] == Dziɖuɖu == [[File:Togbe Wiah Kwasi II.jpg|thumb|right|Tɔgbe Wiah Kwasi II
Ʋegbe Kpalime Fiaga
(Tso 2010)]] Ʋegbe dukɔa ƒe dziɖula enye woƒe Fiaga. Amesi eny Fiaga fifia enye Aƒetɔ Silas Wiah. Eƒe kpukpo ŋukɔ enye Tɔgbe Wiah Kwasi II. Woɖoe Fiaga le Masa 2010 me.[http://southdayi.ghanadistricts.gov.gh/?arrow=nws&read=34721 GhanaDistricts.Gov.Gh] Ʋegbe Kpalime le South Dayi Distrikt me si ƒe dugã enye [[Kpeve]]. Ghana dukɔa ƒe zimenɔla na distrikt la enye [[Kafui Bekui]]. == Xlẽ esiawo hã == * [[Kpalime dukɔawo]] * [[Kafui Bekui]] == Afisi wotsɔ nyawo tsoe == {{Reflist}} == Nuxexlẽwo kple nutatawo tso teƒe bubuwo == * [http://southdayi.ghanadistricts.gov.gh/ South Dayi District Official website] * [http://maps.msn.com/%28tyjzxszmjpjceivjextxxkrf%29/map.aspx?L=WLD&C=6.65048%2c0.33266&A=215.00000&P=|A0EFC7|&TI=Wegbe%2c+Ghana MSN Map] * [http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=6.65000,+0.34112&sll=6.649944,0.341606&sspn=0.009804,0.021136&ie=UTF8&ll=6.649603,0.326843&spn=0.156866,0.468979&t=h&z=12 Google maps] {{Kpalime dukɔwo}} [[Category:Ghana duwo]]

[[File:Lion, Masai Mara, Kenya.jpg|thumb|Dzatatsu]] [[File:Lioness.jpg|thumb|Dzatanɔ]] Dzata nyé gbemelã sesẽtɔwo dometɔ ɖeka. Enye lã ɖuʋulɛ̃ . Tso keke gbaɖegbe ke la, woda ŋkɔ ɖe edzi be enye lãwo ƒe fia. Ŋkɔ sia dzee vavã elabena enye lã dziŋɔ wɔdã aɖe si ɖu gbemelãwo katã kloe dzi.
==Dzedzeme alo Nɔnɔme== Dzata ɖi [[Dadi|dadi]] le go geɖe me. Enye lã triakɔ̃ aɖe si afɔ kako ene li na. Afɔdidɛ atɔ̃ siwo nu fe ɖaɖɛwo le la le eƒe afɔawo nu. Eƒe fuwo biã eye asike legbee aɖe si ŋu fu kpoyoo aɖe le la li nɛ. Eƒe ta lolo ŋku eve siwo kpɔkpɔ doa vɔvɔ̃ na ame la le ta ŋu nɛ. Dzatatsu to fu ɖe kɔ me fũ. Woyɔa fu sia be '''kɔdza'''. Dzatanɔ ya metoa '''kɔdza''' o.
{{stub}} [[Category:Lãwo]] [[Category:Gbemelãwo]]

revision.text:
'''Lododo''' alo '''Lododowo''' (Eŋlisigbeme [[:en:Proverb|Proverbs]] ) nye nya siwo miegblɔna kuɖe agbe aɖe si ame ɖe nɔ la ŋu. Enu enu la, nya siawo nyea nuxɔxlɔ̃ na amewo eye wodea sesẽ lãme na nunyuiwɔlawo.
==Lododo ƒe kpɔɖeŋu aɖewo== Lododo ƒe kpɔɖeŋu aɖewoe nye: *Vi gbã abɔbɔgo me gbã klo go o. *Ɖevi ka aplẽ gã mekaa nya gã o. *Nunya adidoe asi me tu ne o. *Kokloxɔ vuvu mekpe na ŋu na koklo o. *Ne edidi ʋu hã etsɔ ko woyɔne. *Ha be ŋdi tsie nye nyia. *Agbenɔxevi megbea fu megbea fuma to o. *Gbɔ̃ tokpo ye xlɔŋu via. *Ahlɔ̃e medoa nyi fɔkpa o. *Ha be mele lolo me o, tsivivi mee wole. <!--*Koklo be ɣlidola wo xɔna na.--> *Koklo metsɔa ƒu dome vea avu o. *Koklo be kɔ gbɔe agbe le. *Mɔdidi megbea du nu yi na o. *Gbɔ̃sikɛ menɔa gbɔ̃ ŋgɔ o. *Haho metsɔa tɔ o. *Ta menɔanyi klo dɔa kuku o. *Gli matsɔ amegbɔ wome dea mee o. *Wome da kalami ɖe dadi gbɔ o. *Dzigbɔdi wo tsɔ xɔa nu le fia si. *Avu ɖu ƒu me dua ga o. *Sabala le nogo gake mɔ le eme. *Alegeli be ekpo ɖe megbetɔwo dzi. *Vivi mevɔ na le agɔ kuŋu hafi wotsɔne ƒua gbe o. *Dadi be nusi avu kpɔ hafi do ɣli, ye yekpɔna mia ŋku ɖedzi. *Melege melegea ɖewo tsia ɖi ame. *Dzea ʋa ɖia, aʋa mesi nɛ o. *Makpɔƒle metsia asime o. *Ta ɖeka meɖea aɖaŋu o. *Dumenyo mesɔa aƒe o. *Avulélae xɔa kɔ. *Ame eve metsia bome o. *Nunyui wɔla ƒe ta me tsia bame o. *Klo be wó be ye neva kpɔ yegbe, ye na be ye ƒe ta tsi gome. {{stub}}

Wickiana
revision.text:
[[Image:Wickiana5.jpg|thumb|200px|Dzotɔtɔ adzetɔ etɔ le [[Baden, Switzerland|Baden]] (1585).]] '''Wickiana''' nye nyadzɔdzɔwo ƒe ƒuƒoƒo kuɖe nusiwo le dzɔdzɔm fifia si sɔ kple nusiwo dzɔ le senturi wuiade lia me siwo nɔ amaŋgba deka dzi kple agbale gawo, mɔme nutatawo, azi nu ŋɔŋlɔwo kple nutatawo. Fifiame gbale drodo nuwo nye nu vevitɔwo kuɖe nane siwo wɔ la nu, si wo yɔ le Switzerland be Reformation. [[Johann Jakob Wick]] (1522-1588), si megbe wotsɔna nusiawo ƒe ƒuƒoƒo, nye Mawununɔla le Predigerkirche eye wonɔ kadodome kple [[Zürich]] dɔyɔƒe tso 1552 eye woga nye [[Archdeacon]] evelia le eyiyi ma me, kpe ɖe nunɔle [[Grossmünster]] le [[Zürich]] tso 1557. E ƒoƒu eye woɖo nyadzɔdzɔ gbale siawo ɖe nɔnɔme nyuitɔ me le ƒe 1559 kple 1588 dome, etsɔ nububuwo ha de wo nɔƒewo le ƒe 1505 lɔƒo vaseɖe 1559 le ye ƒe nuƒoƒuawo me.
<!-- Wick’s collection is bound in 24 [[Folio (printing)|folio volumes]], which were housed in the Grossmünster Stiftsbibliothek after Wick’s death in 1588 and subsequently transferred to the Zürich Stadtbibliothek in 1836. In addition to a vast number of prints from the German-speaking countries, the collection also contains 52 items in other languages. Many of the sheets emanate from the most important centres for printing and book production at that period – [[Augsburg]], [[Nürnberg]] and [[Strassburg]].
In pictures and texts, the documents bear witness to contemporary life, reporting on such phenomena as natural occurrences – comets, earthquakes and floods - , physical deformities in animals and humans, sensational crimes and political events of the time. For example, the comet of 1577 is described as “terrible and wondrous” (“schrecklich und wunderbarlich”). The collection can be regarded as manifesting the climate of crisis at a time of religious and political turmoil: [[Huldrych Zwingli]] (died 1531) had recently predicted the end of the world. Wick’s collection of documents may have been regarded by him and his contemporaries as harbingers of the Last Judgement.
==Access== 439 illustrated broadsheets (woodcuts), 429 of which belong to the original collection. 10 were added later. In 1925, these illustrated broadsheets were removed from Johann Jakob Wick’s manuscript volumes and archived separately in the Department of Prints and Drawings of the Zentralbibliothek Zürich (Graphische Sammlung). All the rest of the documents, Wick’s entire collection, are housed in the Department of Manuscripts in the [[Zentralbibliothek Zürich]] (Handschriftenabteilung). -->
== Kpɔ esiawo hã == Tso Eŋlisi Wikipeɖia *[[:en:Swiss illustrated chronicles|Swiss illustrated chronicles]] *[[:en:History of Zürich|History of Zürich]] *[[:en:Historiography of Switzerland|Historiography of Switzerland]] *[[:en:Reformation in Switzerland|Reformation in Switzerland]]
==Kpɔɖeŋuwo== <gallery> File:Wickiana Heuschrecke.jpg|Abɔtre/Abɔtri File:Wickiana Treppensturz.jpg|Monk Bastian Hegner dze anyi eye woku le Rapperswil le [[Ademakpɔxe]] 12, 1561 me. File:Wickiana Kind Maschwanden.jpg|Eha le ɖevi aɖe eye wowui le [[Maschwanden]]. File:Wickiana Mönche.jpg|Wo ƒo monk eve vevie le Geneva ɖe amebaba ta. File:Zentralbibliothek Zürich - Von einem schrecklichen und wunderbarlichen Cometen so sich den Dienstag nach Martini dieses lauffenden M D LXXViJ Jahrs am Himmel erzeiget hat - 000003593.jpg| <!--[[Great Comet of 1577]], Prag, November 12, 1577--> </gallery>
==Nugɔmekuku tsoƒewo== *M. Senn, '' Die Wickiana. Johann Jakob Wicks Nachrichtensammlung aus dem 16. Jahrhundert'', Zürich 1975. *Franz Matthias Mauelshagen, ''Wunderkammer auf Papier. Die Wickiana zwischen Reformation und Volksglaube'', Diss. Univ. Zürich, Zürich 2008. *Wolfgang Harms, Michael Schilling (eds.), ''Die Wickiana. Die Sammlung der Zentralbibliothek Zürich'', Tübingen 1997–2005.

|- !align="left" valign="top"|[[ISO 3166]] |colspan=2 valign=top| GH-TV-BI |} The '''Biakoye District''' is one of the twenty-five (25) [[District|districts]] in the [[Volta Region]]. Biakoye district capital and administrative centre is [[Nkonya Ahenkro]]. == History == The Biakoye District was created in 2008 and inaugurated officially on 29 February 2008. == Notable people == One of the notable citizens of the District is [[Ave K. Kludze]], a [[NASA]] rocket scientist who was honoured at the village of Gbi [[Kpeme]], near Nkonya Ahenkro during a festival.[http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/artikel.php?ID=162976 Gbi-Kpeme honours rocket scientist] == Footnotes == {{reflist}} == References and external links == * [http://www.ghanadistricts.com/districts/?news&r=7&_=184 Biakoye District] at GhanaDistricts.com. {{Volta Region, Ghana}} [[Category:Districts of Volta Region]] [[Category:States and territories established in 2008]]

Tagbo Tsidzaƒe
revision.text: [[File:Tagbo Falls Ghana.jpg|thumb|Tagbo Tsidzaƒe le Liate Wote]] '''Tagbo Falls''' nye tsidzaƒe si teɖe [[Afadzto]] gbɔ le [[Ghana]], ele Liati Wote, si anɔ abe kilometa 27 le [[Hohoe]] ƒe ɣedzeƒe . Tsidzaƒe sia dudu na le doƒe vovowo me, doƒe mamletɔ anɔ abe meta 60 ƒe kɔkɔme ene . Ave ƒo xla teƒe sia.

revision.comment: Nuɖuɖuwo ƒe hatsotso.
ŋlɔ axa yeye Waakye
revision.text:
[[File:Ghanaian Wache (Waakye) cuisine food.jpg|thumb|right|Waakye le agbame]]
'''Waakye''' nye nuɖuɖu bɔbɔ aɖe le [[Ghana]] si ame sia ame kloe ɖuna. Wo ɖaa waakye le aƒeme gake zi geɖe la, edzralawo ɖo na asi ɖe lɔri mɔtɔwo alo xɔsɔe aɖe me kpli. Waakye ɖaɖa do na go tso mɔlu kple ayi si woɖo dzodzi zi ɖekae me.
'''Waakye''' si woateŋu aɖu le ɖe ŋdi alo ŋdɔ nuɖuɖu teƒe. Wo ɖua waakye kple nudonui siawo dometɔ ɖeka alo wo ƒe agbɔsɔsɔme, kelewele, akpa tɔtɔ, abladzo tɔtɔ, koklozi ɖaɖa, koklola tɔtɔ.
[[Category:Nuɖuɖuwo]]

revision.text:
{|class="toccolours" cellpadding="10" rules="cols" width=59% ! Mia Denyigba Lɔ̃lɔ̃ la |- ! colspan="2" bgcolor="red" |First stanza |- |width=2%|
Mia denyigba lɔ̃lɔ̃ la
Enu wonye woa ƒoa sia?
Mia tɔgbuiwo tsɔ woƒe
agbe gble ɖe eta xɔe nami
Eɖo nye kpli woha dzi
be mia wɔ miatɔ sinu
Nuvevi nyenye, diɖoɖo,
kple ame ɖokui tɔdzidzi,
Bu miaƒe azɔli hegble mia denyigba alegbegbe.
|- !colspan="2" bgcolor="yellow"|Second stanza |- |width=2%|
Agbalemenunya ƒuƒlu
Loo hotsui kpɔkpɔ guduu
Kple agbe yaka nɔnɔ
Meyina kple anyigba lɔ̃lɔ̃ o
Ta bɔbɔ kple amelɔame
Nyui didi na amesiame
Kple lã dodo ame ɖokui
Na xɔ̃lɔ̃ viviwo ƒe nyonyo ko
Woawo mee tomefafa
Kple ŋgɔyiyi nyui wodzɔ tso.
|- !colspan="2" bgcolor="green"|Chorus |- |width=2%|
Denyigba wo nyonyo
Denyigba wo gbegble
Alesi newɔe la
Sigbe ke woa nɔ daa
|}
